var book = {
	"name": "Proverbs",
	"numChapters": 31,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16402A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16402A\"></sup>proverbs of Solomon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16402B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16402B\"></sup>the son of David, king of Israel:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16403C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16403C\"></sup>wisdom and instruction,To discern the sayings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16403D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16403D\"></sup>understanding,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16404E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16404E\"></sup>receive instruction in wise behavior,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16404F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16404F\"></sup>Righteousness, justice and equity;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>To give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16405G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16405G\"></sup>prudence to the naive,To the youth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16405H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16405H\"></sup>knowledge and discretion,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A wise man will hear and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16406I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16406I\"></sup>increase in learning,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16406J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16406J\"></sup>man of understanding will acquire wise counsel,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>To understand a proverb and a figure,The words of the wise and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16407K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16407K\"></sup>riddles.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16408L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16408L\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the beginning of knowledge;Fools despise wisdom and instruction.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16409M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16409M\"></sup>Hear, my son, your father’s instructionAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16409N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16409N\"></sup>do not forsake your mother’s teaching;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Indeed, they are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16410O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16410O\"></sup>graceful wreath to your headAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16410P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16410P\"></sup>ornaments about your neck.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My son, if sinners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16411Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16411Q\"></sup>entice you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16411R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16411R\"></sup>Do not consent.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they say, “Come with us,Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16412S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16412S\"></sup>lie in wait for blood,Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16412T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16412T\"></sup>ambush the innocent without cause;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16413U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16413U\"></sup>swallow them alive like Sheol,Even whole, as those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16413V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16413V\"></sup>go down to the pit;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>We will find all <i>kinds</i> of precious wealth,We will fill our houses with spoil;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Throw in your lot with us,We shall all have one purse,”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16416W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16416W\"></sup>do not walk in the way with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16416X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16416X\"></sup>Keep your feet from their path,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16417Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16417Y\"></sup>their feet run to evilAnd they hasten to shed blood.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Indeed, it is useless to spread the <i>baited</i> netIn the sight of any bird;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16419Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16419Z\"></sup>lie in wait for their own blood;They ambush their own lives.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So are the ways of everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16420AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16420AA\"></sup>gains by violence;It takes away the life of its possessors.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16421AB\"></sup>Wisdom shouts in the street,She lifts her voice in the square;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>At the head of the noisy <i>streets</i> she cries out;At the entrance of the gates in the city she utters her sayings:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“How long, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16423AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16423AC\"></sup>naive ones, will you love being simple-minded?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16423AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16423AD\"></sup>scoffers delight themselves in scoffingAnd fools <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16423AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16423AE\"></sup>hate knowledge?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Turn to my reproof,Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16424AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16424AF\"></sup>pour out my spirit on you;I will make my words known to you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16425AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16425AG\"></sup>I called and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16425AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16425AH\"></sup>refused,I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16425AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16425AI\"></sup>stretched out my hand and no one paid attention;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16426AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16426AJ\"></sup>neglected all my counselAnd did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16426AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16426AK\"></sup>want my reproof;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16427AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16427AL\"></sup>laugh at your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16427AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16427AM\"></sup>calamity;I will mock when your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16427AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16427AN\"></sup>dread comes,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When your dread comes like a stormAnd your calamity comes like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16428AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16428AO\"></sup>whirlwind,When distress and anguish come upon you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16429AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16429AP\"></sup>call on me, but I will not answer;They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16429AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16429AQ\"></sup>seek me diligently but they will not find me,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16430AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16430AR\"></sup>hated knowledgeAnd did not choose the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16431AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16431AS\"></sup>would not accept my counsel,They spurned all my reproof.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“So they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16432AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16432AT\"></sup>eat of the fruit of their own wayAnd be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16432AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16432AU\"></sup>satiated with their own devices.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16433AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16433AV\"></sup>waywardness of the naive will kill them,And the complacency of fools will destroy them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16434AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16434AW\"></sup>he who listens to me shall live securelyAnd will be at ease from the dread of evil.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>My son, if you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16435A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16435A\"></sup>receive my wordsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16435B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16435B\"></sup>treasure my commandments within you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16436C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16436C\"></sup>Make your ear attentive to wisdom,Incline your heart to understanding;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For if you cry for discernment,Lift your voice for understanding;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If you seek her as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16438D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16438D\"></sup>silverAnd search for her as for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16438E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16438E\"></sup>hidden treasures;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then you will discern the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16439F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16439F\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And discover the knowledge of God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16440G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16440G\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives wisdom;From His mouth <i>come</i> knowledge and understanding.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He stores up sound wisdom for the upright;<i>He is</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16441H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16441H\"></sup>shield to those who walk in integrity,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Guarding the paths of justice,And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16442I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16442I\"></sup>preserves the way of His godly ones.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then you will discern <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16443J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16443J\"></sup>righteousness and justiceAnd equity <i>and</i> every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16443K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16443K\"></sup>good course.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16444L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16444L\"></sup>wisdom will enter your heartAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16444M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16444M\"></sup>knowledge will be pleasant to your soul;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Discretion will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16445N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16445N\"></sup>guard you,Understanding will watch over you,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16446O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16446O\"></sup>deliver you from the way of evil,From the man who speaks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16446P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16446P\"></sup>perverse things;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>From those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16447Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16447Q\"></sup>leave the paths of uprightnessTo walk in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16447R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16447R\"></sup>ways of darkness;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16448S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16448S\"></sup>delight in doing evilAnd rejoice in the perversity of evil;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Whose paths are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16449T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16449T\"></sup>crooked,And who are devious in their ways;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16450U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16450U\"></sup>deliver you from the strange woman,From the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16450V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16450V\"></sup>adulteress who flatters with her words;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>That leaves the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16451W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16451W\"></sup>companion of her youthAnd forgets the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16451X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16451X\"></sup>covenant of her God;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16452Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16452Y\"></sup>her house sinks down to deathAnd her tracks <i>lead</i> to the dead;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>None <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16453Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16453Z\"></sup>who go to her return again,Nor do they reach the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16453AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16453AA\"></sup>paths of life.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16454AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16454AB\"></sup>walk in the way of good menAnd keep to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16454AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16454AC\"></sup>paths of the righteous.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16455AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16455AD\"></sup>the upright will live in the landAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16455AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16455AE\"></sup>the blameless will remain in it;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16456AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16456AF\"></sup>the wicked will be cut off from the landAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16456AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16456AG\"></sup>the treacherous will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16456AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16456AH\"></sup>uprooted from it."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16457A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16457A\"></sup>do not forget my teaching,But let your heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16457B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16457B\"></sup>keep my commandments;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16458C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16458C\"></sup>length of days and years of lifeAnd peace they will add to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16459D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16459D\"></sup>kindness and truth leave you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16459E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16459E\"></sup>Bind them around your neck,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16459F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16459F\"></sup>Write them on the tablet of your heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16460G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16460G\"></sup>find favor and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16460H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16460H\"></sup>good reputeIn the sight of God and man.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16461I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16461I\"></sup>Trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with all your heartAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16461J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16461J\"></sup>do not lean on your own understanding.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In all your ways <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16462K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16462K\"></sup>acknowledge Him,And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16462L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16462L\"></sup>make your paths straight.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16463M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16463M\"></sup>Do not be wise in your own eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16463N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16463N\"></sup>Fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and turn away from evil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16464O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16464O\"></sup>healing to your bodyAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16464P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16464P\"></sup>refreshment to your bones.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16465Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16465Q\"></sup>Honor the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from your wealthAnd from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16465R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16465R\"></sup>first of all your produce;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16466S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16466S\"></sup>barns will be filled with plentyAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16466T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16466T\"></sup>vats will overflow with new wine.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16467U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16467U\"></sup>My son, do not reject the discipline of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Or loathe His reproof,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16468V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16468V\"></sup>whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves He reproves,Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16468W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16468W\"></sup>as a father <i>corrects</i> the son in whom he delights.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16469X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16469X\"></sup>How blessed is the man who finds wisdomAnd the man who gains understanding.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16470Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16470Y\"></sup>profit is better than the profit of silverAnd her gain better than fine gold.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16471Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16471Z\"></sup>more precious than jewels;And nothing you desire compares with her.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16472AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16472AA\"></sup>Long life is in her right hand;In her left hand are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16472AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16472AB\"></sup>riches and honor.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16473AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16473AC\"></sup>ways are pleasant waysAnd all her paths are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16473AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16473AD\"></sup>peace.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16474AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16474AE\"></sup>tree of life to those who take hold of her,And happy are all who hold her fast.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16475AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16475AF\"></sup>by wisdom founded the earth,By understanding He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16475AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16475AG\"></sup>established the heavens.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>By His knowledge the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16476AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16476AH\"></sup>deeps were broken upAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16476AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16476AI\"></sup>skies drip with dew.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16477AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16477AJ\"></sup>let them not vanish from your sight;Keep sound wisdom and discretion,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16478AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16478AK\"></sup>life to your soulAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16478AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16478AL\"></sup>adornment to your neck.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16479AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16479AM\"></sup>walk in your way securelyAnd your foot will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16479AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16479AN\"></sup>stumble.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16480AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16480AO\"></sup>lie down, you will not be afraid;When you lie down, your sleep will be sweet.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16481AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16481AP\"></sup>Do not be afraid of sudden fearNor of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16481AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16481AQ\"></sup>onslaught of the wicked when it comes;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your confidenceAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16482AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16482AR\"></sup>keep your foot from being caught.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16483AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16483AS\"></sup>Do not withhold good from those to whom it is due,When it is in your power to do <i>it</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16484AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16484AT\"></sup>Do not say to your neighbor, “Go, and come back,And tomorrow I will give <i>it</i>,”When you have it with you.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16485AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16485AU\"></sup>Do not devise harm against your neighbor,While he lives securely beside you.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16486AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16486AV\"></sup>Do not contend with a man without cause,If he has done you no harm.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16487AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16487AW\"></sup>Do not envy a man of violenceAnd do not choose any of his ways.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16488AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16488AX\"></sup>devious are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;But He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16488AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16488AY\"></sup>intimate with the upright.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16489AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16489AZ\"></sup>curse of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is on the house of the wicked,But He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16489BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16489BA\"></sup>blesses the dwelling of the righteous.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16490BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16490BB\"></sup>He scoffs at the scoffers,Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16490BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16490BC\"></sup>He gives grace to the afflicted.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16491BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16491BD\"></sup>The wise will inherit honor,But fools display dishonor."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Hear, <i>O</i> sons, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16492A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16492A\"></sup>instruction of a father,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16492B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16492B\"></sup>give attention that you may gain understanding,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I give you sound <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16493C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16493C\"></sup>teaching;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16493D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16493D\"></sup>Do not abandon my instruction.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When I was a son to my father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16494E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16494E\"></sup>Tender and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16494F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16494F\"></sup>the only son in the sight of my mother,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16495G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16495G\"></sup>taught me and said to me,“Let your heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16495H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16495H\"></sup>hold fast my words;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16495I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16495I\"></sup>Keep my commandments and live;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16496J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16496J\"></sup>Acquire wisdom! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16496K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16496K\"></sup>Acquire understanding!Do not forget nor turn away from the words of my mouth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Do not forsake her, and she will guard you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16497L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16497L\"></sup>Love her, and she will watch over you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16498M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16498M\"></sup>The beginning of wisdom <i>is</i>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16498N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16498N\"></sup>Acquire wisdom;And with all your acquiring, get understanding.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16499O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16499O\"></sup>Prize her, and she will exalt you;She will honor you if you embrace her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“She will place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16500P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16500P\"></sup>on your head a garland of grace;She will present you with a crown of beauty.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hear, my son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16501Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16501Q\"></sup>accept my sayingsAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16501R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16501R\"></sup>years of your life will be many.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16502S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16502S\"></sup>directed you in the way of wisdom;I have led you in upright paths.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you walk, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16503T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16503T\"></sup>steps will not be impeded;And if you run, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16503U\"></sup>will not stumble.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16504V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16504V\"></sup>Take hold of instruction; do not let go.Guard her, for she is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16504W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16504W\"></sup>life.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16505X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16505X\"></sup>Do not enter the path of the wickedAnd do not proceed in the way of evil men.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Avoid it, do not pass by it;Turn away from it and pass on.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16507Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16507Y\"></sup>cannot sleep unless they do evil;And they are robbed of sleep unless they make <i>someone</i> stumble.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16508Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16508Z\"></sup>eat the bread of wickednessAnd drink the wine of violence.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16509AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16509AA\"></sup>path of the righteous is like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16509AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16509AB\"></sup>light of dawn,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16509AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16509AC\"></sup>shines brighter and brighter until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16509AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16509AD\"></sup>full day.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16510AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16510AE\"></sup>way of the wicked is like darkness;They do not know over what they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16510AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16510AF\"></sup>stumble.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16511AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16511AG\"></sup>give attention to my words;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16511AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16511AH\"></sup>Incline your ear to my sayings.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16512AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16512AI\"></sup>Do not let them depart from your sight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16512AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16512AJ\"></sup>Keep them in the midst of your heart.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16513AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16513AK\"></sup>life to those who find themAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16513AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16513AL\"></sup>health to all their body.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Watch over your heart with all diligence,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16514AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16514AM\"></sup>from it <i>flow</i> the springs of life.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Put away from you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16515AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16515AN\"></sup>deceitful mouthAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16515AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16515AO\"></sup>put devious speech far from you.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let your eyes look directly aheadAnd let your gaze be fixed straight in front of you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16517AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16517AP\"></sup>Watch the path of your feetAnd all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16517AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16517AQ\"></sup>ways will be established.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16518AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16518AR\"></sup>Do not turn to the right nor to the left;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16518AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16518AS\"></sup>Turn your foot from evil."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16519A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16519A\"></sup>give attention to my wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16519B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16519B\"></sup>Incline your ear to my understanding;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>That you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16520C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16520C\"></sup>observe discretionAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16520D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16520D\"></sup>lips may reserve knowledge.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the lips of an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16521E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16521E\"></sup>adulteress <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16521F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16521F\"></sup>drip honeyAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16521G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16521G\"></sup>smoother than oil is her speech;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But in the end she is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16522H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16522H\"></sup>bitter as wormwood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16522I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16522I\"></sup>Sharp as a two-edged sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Her feet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16523J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16523J\"></sup>go down to death,Her steps take hold of Sheol.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>She does not ponder the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16524K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16524K\"></sup>path of life;Her ways are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16524L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16524L\"></sup>unstable, she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16524M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16524M\"></sup>does not know <i>it</i>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16525N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16525N\"></sup>Now then, <i>my</i> sons, listen to meAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16525O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16525O\"></sup>do not depart from the words of my mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16526P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16526P\"></sup>Keep your way far from herAnd do not go near the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16526Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16526Q\"></sup>door of her house,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or you will give your vigor to othersAnd your years to the cruel one;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And strangers will be filled with your strengthAnd your hard-earned goods <i>will go</i> to the house of an alien;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And you groan at your final end,When your flesh and your body are consumed;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And you say, “How I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16530R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16530R\"></sup>hated instruction!And my heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16530S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16530S\"></sup>spurned reproof!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I have not listened to the voice of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16531T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16531T\"></sup>teachers,Nor inclined my ear to my instructors!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I was almost in utter ruinIn the midst of the assembly and congregation.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Drink water from your own cisternAnd fresh water from your own well.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Should your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16534U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16534U\"></sup>springs be dispersed abroad,Streams of water in the streets?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let them be yours aloneAnd not for strangers with you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16536V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16536V\"></sup>fountain be blessed,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16536W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16536W\"></sup>rejoice in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16536X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16536X\"></sup>wife of your youth.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>As</i> a loving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16537Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16537Y\"></sup>hind and a graceful doe,Let her breasts satisfy you at all times;Be exhilarated always with her love.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For why should you, my son, be exhilarated with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16538Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16538Z\"></sup>adulteressAnd embrace the bosom of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16538AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16538AA\"></sup>foreigner?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16539AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16539AB\"></sup>ways of a man are before the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16539AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16539AC\"></sup>watches all his paths.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16540AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16540AD\"></sup>own iniquities will capture the wicked,And he will be held with the cords of his sin.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16541AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16541AE\"></sup>die for lack of instruction,And in the greatness of his folly he will go astray."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>My son, if you have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16542A\"></sup>surety for your neighbor,Have given a pledge for a stranger,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><i>If</i> you have been snared with the words of your mouth,Have been caught with the words of your mouth,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do this then, my son, and deliver yourself;Since you have come into the hand of your neighbor,Go, humble yourself, and importune your neighbor.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Give no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16545B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16545B\"></sup>sleep to your eyes,Nor slumber to your eyelids;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Deliver yourself like a gazelle from <i>the hunter’s</i> handAnd like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16546C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16546C\"></sup>bird from the hand of the fowler.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Go to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16547D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16547D\"></sup>ant, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16547E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16547E\"></sup>sluggard,Observe her ways and be wise,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Which, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16548F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16548F\"></sup>no chief,Officer or ruler,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Prepares her food <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16549G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16549G\"></sup>in the summer<i>And</i> gathers her provision in the harvest.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How long will you lie down, O sluggard?When will you arise from your sleep?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16551H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16551H\"></sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,A little folding of the hands to rest”—",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16552I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16552I\"></sup>Your poverty will come in like a vagabondAnd your need like an armed man.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16553J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16553J\"></sup>worthless person, a wicked man,Is the one who walks with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16553K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16553K\"></sup>perverse mouth,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16554L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16554L\"></sup>winks with his eyes, who signals with his feet,Who points with his fingers;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who <i>with</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16555M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16555M\"></sup>perversity in his heart continually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16555N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16555N\"></sup>devises evil,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16555O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16555O\"></sup>spreads strife.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16556P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16556P\"></sup>his calamity will come suddenly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16556Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16556Q\"></sup>Instantly he will be broken and there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16556R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16556R\"></sup>no healing.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>There are six things which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hates,Yes, seven which are an abomination to Him:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16558S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16558S\"></sup>Haughty eyes, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16558T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16558T\"></sup>lying tongue,And hands that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16558U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16558U\"></sup>shed innocent blood,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A heart that devises <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16559V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16559V\"></sup>wicked plans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16559W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16559W\"></sup>Feet that run rapidly to evil,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16560X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16560X\"></sup>false witness <i>who</i> utters lies,And one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16560Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16560Y\"></sup>spreads strife among brothers.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16561Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16561Z\"></sup>My son, observe the commandment of your fatherAnd do not forsake the teaching of your mother;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16562AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16562AA\"></sup>Bind them continually on your heart;Tie them around your neck.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16563AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16563AB\"></sup>walk about, they will guide you;When you sleep, they will watch over you;And when you awake, they will talk to you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16564AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16564AC\"></sup>the commandment is a lamp and the teaching is light;And reproofs for discipline are the way of life",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16565AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16565AD\"></sup>keep you from the evil woman,From the smooth tongue of the adulteress.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16566AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16566AE\"></sup>Do not desire her beauty in your heart,Nor let her capture you with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16566AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16566AF\"></sup>eyelids.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16567AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16567AG\"></sup>on account of a harlot <i>one is reduced</i> to a loaf of bread,And an adulteress <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16567AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16567AH\"></sup>hunts for the precious life.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Can a man take fire in his bosomAnd his clothes not be burned?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Or can a man walk on hot coalsAnd his feet not be scorched?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So is the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16570AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16570AI\"></sup>goes in to his neighbor’s wife;Whoever touches her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16570AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16570AJ\"></sup>will not go unpunished.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Men do not despise a thief if he stealsTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16571AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16571AK\"></sup>satisfy himself when he is hungry;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But when he is found, he must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16572AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16572AL\"></sup>repay sevenfold;He must give all the substance of his house.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The one who commits adultery with a woman is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16573AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16573AM\"></sup>lacking sense;He who would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16573AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16573AN\"></sup>destroy himself does it.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Wounds and disgrace he will find,And his reproach will not be blotted out.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16575AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16575AO\"></sup>jealousy enrages a man,And he will not spare in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16575AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16575AP\"></sup>day of vengeance.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>He will not accept any ransom,Nor will he be satisfied though you give many gifts."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16577A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16577A\"></sup>keep my wordsAnd treasure my commandments within you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16578B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16578B\"></sup>Keep my commandments and live,And my teaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16578C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16578C\"></sup>as the apple of your eye.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16579D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16579D\"></sup>Bind them on your fingers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16579E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16579E\"></sup>Write them on the tablet of your heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to wisdom, “You are my sister,”And call understanding <i>your</i> intimate friend;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>That they may keep you from an adulteress,From the foreigner who flatters with her words.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16582F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16582F\"></sup>at the window of my houseI looked out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16582G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16582G\"></sup>through my lattice,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I saw among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16583H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16583H\"></sup>naive,<i>And</i> discerned among the youthsA young man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16583I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16583I\"></sup>lacking sense,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Passing through the street near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16584J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16584J\"></sup>her corner;And he takes the way to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16584K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16584K\"></sup>her house,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16585L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16585L\"></sup>twilight, in the evening,In the middle of the night and <i>in</i> the darkness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And behold, a woman <i>comes</i> to meet him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16586M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16586M\"></sup>Dressed as a harlot and cunning of heart.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>She is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16587N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16587N\"></sup>boisterous and rebellious,Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16587O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16587O\"></sup>feet do not remain at home;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>She is</i> now in the streets, now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16588P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16588P\"></sup>in the squares,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16588Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16588Q\"></sup>lurks by every corner.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So she seizes him and kisses himAnd with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16589R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16589R\"></sup>brazen face she says to him:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I was due to offer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16590S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16590S\"></sup>peace offerings;Today I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16590T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16590T\"></sup>paid my vows.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Therefore I have come out to meet you,To seek your presence earnestly, and I have found you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I have spread my couch with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16592U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16592U\"></sup>coverings,With colored <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16592V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16592V\"></sup>linens of Egypt.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I have sprinkled my bedWith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16593W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16593W\"></sup>myrrh, aloes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16593X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16593X\"></sup>cinnamon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Come, let us drink our fill of love until morning;Let us delight ourselves with caresses.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“For my husband is not at home,He has gone on a long journey;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He has taken a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16596Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16596Y\"></sup>bag of money with him,At the full moon he will come home.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>With her many persuasions she entices him;With her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16597Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16597Z\"></sup>flattering lips she seduces him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Suddenly he follows herAs an ox goes to the slaughter,Or as <i>one in</i> fetters to the discipline of a fool,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Until an arrow pierces through his liver;As a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16599AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16599AA\"></sup>bird hastens to the snare,So he does not know that it <i>will cost him</i> his life.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now therefore, <i>my</i> sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16600AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16600AB\"></sup>listen to me,And pay attention to the words of my mouth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not let your heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16601AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16601AC\"></sup>turn aside to her ways,Do not stray into her paths.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For many are the victims she has cast down,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16602AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16602AD\"></sup>numerous are all her slain.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16603AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16603AE\"></sup>house is the way to Sheol,Descending to the chambers of death."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16604A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16604A\"></sup>wisdom call,And understanding lift up her voice?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On top of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16605B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16605B\"></sup>the heights beside the way,Where the paths meet, she takes her stand;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Beside the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16606C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16606C\"></sup>gates, at the opening to the city,At the entrance of the doors, she cries out:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“To you, O men, I call,And my voice is to the sons of men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16608D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16608D\"></sup>naive ones, understand prudence;And, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16608E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16608E\"></sup>fools, understand wisdom.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Listen, for I will speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16609F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16609F\"></sup>noble things;And the opening of my lips <i>will reveal</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16609G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16609G\"></sup>right things.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16610H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16610H\"></sup>mouth will utter truth;And wickedness is an abomination to my lips.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“All the utterances of my mouth are in righteousness;There is nothing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16611I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16611I\"></sup>crooked or perverted in them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“They are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16612J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16612J\"></sup>straightforward to him who understands,And right to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16612K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16612K\"></sup>find knowledge.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Take my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16613L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16613L\"></sup>instruction and not silver,And knowledge rather than choicest gold.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“For wisdom is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16614M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16614M\"></sup>better than jewels;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16614N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16614N\"></sup>all desirable things cannot compare with her.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, wisdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16615O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16615O\"></sup>dwell with prudence,And I find <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16615P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16615P\"></sup>knowledge <i>and</i> discretion.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16616Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16616Q\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is to hate evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16616R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16616R\"></sup>Pride and arrogance and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16616S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16616S\"></sup>the evil wayAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16616T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16616T\"></sup>perverted mouth, I hate.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16617U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16617U\"></sup>Counsel is mine and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16617V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16617V\"></sup>sound wisdom;I am understanding, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16617W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16617W\"></sup>power is mine.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“By me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16618X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16618X\"></sup>kings reign,And rulers decree justice.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“By me princes rule, and nobles,All who judge rightly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16620Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16620Y\"></sup>love those who love me;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16620Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16620Z\"></sup>those who diligently seek me will find me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16621AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16621AA\"></sup>Riches and honor are with me,Enduring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16621AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16621AB\"></sup>wealth and righteousness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“My fruit is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16622AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16622AC\"></sup>better than gold, even pure gold,And my yield <i>better</i> than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16622AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16622AD\"></sup>choicest silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I walk in the way of righteousness,In the midst of the paths of justice,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To endow those who love me with wealth,That I may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16624AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16624AE\"></sup>fill their treasuries.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> possessed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16625AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16625AF\"></sup>at the beginning of His way,Before His works of old.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“From everlasting I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16626AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16626AG\"></sup>established,From the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16626AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16626AH\"></sup>from the earliest times of the earth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“When there were no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16627AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16627AI\"></sup>depths I was brought forth,When there were no springs abounding with water.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16628AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16628AJ\"></sup>Before the mountains were settled,Before the hills I was brought forth;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>While He had not yet made the earth and the fields,Nor the first dust of the world.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“When He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16630AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16630AK\"></sup>established the heavens, I was there,When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16630AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16630AL\"></sup>He inscribed a circle on the face of the deep,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When He made firm the skies above,When the springs of the deep became fixed,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16632AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16632AM\"></sup>He set for the sea its boundarySo that the water would not transgress His command,When He marked out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16632AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16632AN\"></sup>the foundations of the earth;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16633AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16633AO\"></sup>I was beside Him, <i>as</i> a master workman;And I was daily <i>His</i> delight,Rejoicing always before Him,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Rejoicing in the world, His earth,And <i>having</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16634AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16634AP\"></sup>my delight in the sons of men.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Now therefore, <i>O</i> sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16635AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16635AQ\"></sup>listen to me,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16635AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16635AR\"></sup>blessed are they who keep my ways.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16636AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16636AS\"></sup>Heed instruction and be wise,And do not neglect <i>it</i>.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16637AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16637AT\"></sup>Blessed is the man who listens to me,Watching daily at my gates,Waiting at my doorposts.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16638AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16638AU\"></sup>he who finds me finds lifeAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16638AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16638AV\"></sup>obtains favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“But he who sins against me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16639AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16639AW\"></sup>injures himself;All those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16639AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16639AX\"></sup>hate me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16639AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16639AY\"></sup>love death.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Wisdom has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16640A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16640A\"></sup>built her house,She has hewn out her seven pillars;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16641B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16641B\"></sup>prepared her food, she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16641C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16641C\"></sup>mixed her wine;She has also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16641D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16641D\"></sup>set her table;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16642E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16642E\"></sup>sent out her maidens, she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16642F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16642F\"></sup>callsFrom the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16642G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16642G\"></sup>tops of the heights of the city:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16643H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16643H\"></sup>Whoever is naive, let him turn in here!”To him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16643I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16643I\"></sup>lacks understanding she says,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16644J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16644J\"></sup>eat of my foodAnd drink of the wine I have mixed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Forsake <i>your</i> folly and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16645K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16645K\"></sup>live,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16645L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16645L\"></sup>proceed in the way of understanding.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16646M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16646M\"></sup>corrects a scoffer gets dishonor for himself,And he who reproves a wicked man <i>gets</i> insults for himself.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16647N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16647N\"></sup>Do not reprove a scoffer, or he will hate you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16647O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16647O\"></sup>Reprove a wise man and he will love you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Give <i>instruction</i> to a wise man and he will be still wiser,Teach a righteous man and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16648P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16648P\"></sup>increase <i>his</i> learning.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16649Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16649Q\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the beginning of wisdom,And the knowledge of the Holy One is understanding.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16650R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16650R\"></sup>by me your days will be multiplied,And years of life will be added to you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you are wise, you are wise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16651S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16651S\"></sup>for yourself,And if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16651T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16651T\"></sup>scoff, you alone will bear it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The woman of folly is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16652U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16652U\"></sup>boisterous,<i>She is</i> naive and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16652V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16652V\"></sup>knows nothing.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She sits at the doorway of her house,On a seat by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16653W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16653W\"></sup>the high places of the city,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Calling to those who pass by,Who are making their paths straight:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16655X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16655X\"></sup>Whoever is naive, let him turn in here,”And to him who lacks understanding she says,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Stolen water is sweet;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16656Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16656Y\"></sup>bread <i>eaten</i> in secret is pleasant.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But he does not know that the dead are there,<i>That</i> her guests are in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16657Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16657Z\"></sup>depths of Sheol."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16658A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16658A\"></sup>proverbs of Solomon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16658B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16658B\"></sup>A wise son makes a father glad,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16658C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16658C\"></sup>a foolish son is a grief to his mother.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16659D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16659D\"></sup>Ill-gotten gains do not profit,But righteousness delivers from death.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16660E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16660E\"></sup>will not allow the righteous to hunger,But He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16660F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16660F\"></sup>will reject the craving of the wicked.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Poor is he who works with a negligent hand,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16661G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16661G\"></sup>hand of the diligent makes rich.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who gathers in summer is a son who acts wisely,<i>But</i> he who sleeps in harvest is a son who acts shamefully.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16663H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16663H\"></sup>Blessings are on the head of the righteous,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16663I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16663I\"></sup>the mouth of the wicked conceals violence.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16664J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16664J\"></sup>memory of the righteous is blessed,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16664K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16664K\"></sup>the name of the wicked will rot.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16665L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16665L\"></sup>wise of heart will receive commands,But a babbling fool will be ruined.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16666M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16666M\"></sup>who walks in integrity walks securely,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16666N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16666N\"></sup>he who perverts his ways will be found out.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16667O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16667O\"></sup>who winks the eye causes trouble,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16667P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16667P\"></sup>a babbling fool will be ruined.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16668Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16668Q\"></sup>mouth of the righteous is a fountain of life,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16668R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16668R\"></sup>the mouth of the wicked conceals violence.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hatred stirs up strife,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16669S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16669S\"></sup>love covers all transgressions.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16670T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16670T\"></sup>the lips of the discerning, wisdom is found,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16670U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16670U\"></sup>a rod is for the back of him who lacks understanding.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Wise men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16671V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16671V\"></sup>store up knowledge,But with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16671W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16671W\"></sup>the mouth of the foolish, ruin is at hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16672X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16672X\"></sup>rich man’s wealth is his fortress,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16672Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16672Y\"></sup>ruin of the poor is their poverty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16673Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16673Z\"></sup>wages of the righteous is life,The income of the wicked, punishment.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16674AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16674AA\"></sup>is <i>on</i> the path of life who heeds instruction,But he who ignores reproof goes astray.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16675AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16675AB\"></sup>who conceals hatred <i>has</i> lying lips,And he who spreads slander is a fool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16676AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16676AC\"></sup>many words, transgression is unavoidable,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16676AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16676AD\"></sup>he who restrains his lips is wise.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The tongue of the righteous is <i>as</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16677AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16677AE\"></sup>choice silver,The heart of the wicked is <i>worth</i> little.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16678AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16678AF\"></sup>lips of the righteous feed many,But fools <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16678AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16678AG\"></sup>die for lack of understanding.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16679AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16679AH\"></sup>blessing of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that makes rich,And He adds no sorrow to it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Doing wickedness is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16680AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16680AI\"></sup>sport to a fool,And <i>so is</i> wisdom to a man of understanding.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>What <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16681AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16681AJ\"></sup>the wicked fears will come upon him,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16681AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16681AK\"></sup>desire of the righteous will be granted.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16682AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16682AL\"></sup>whirlwind passes, the wicked is no more,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16682AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16682AM\"></sup>righteous <i>has</i> an everlasting foundation.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Like vinegar to the teeth and smoke to the eyes,So is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16683AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16683AN\"></sup>lazy one to those who send him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16684AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16684AO\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> prolongs life,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16684AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16684AP\"></sup>years of the wicked will be shortened.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16685AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16685AQ\"></sup>hope of the righteous is gladness,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16685AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16685AR\"></sup>expectation of the wicked perishes.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16686AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16686AS\"></sup>way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a stronghold to the upright,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16686AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16686AT\"></sup>ruin to the workers of iniquity.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16687AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16687AU\"></sup>righteous will never be shaken,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16687AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16687AV\"></sup>the wicked will not dwell in the land.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16688AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16688AW\"></sup>mouth of the righteous flows with wisdom,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16688AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16688AX\"></sup>perverted tongue will be cut out.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The lips of the righteous bring forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16689AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16689AY\"></sup>what is acceptable,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16689AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16689AZ\"></sup>mouth of the wicked what is perverted."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16690A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16690A\"></sup>false balance is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16690B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16690B\"></sup>just weight is His delight.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16691C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16691C\"></sup>pride comes, then comes dishonor,But with the humble is wisdom.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16692D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16692D\"></sup>integrity of the upright will guide them,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16692E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16692E\"></sup>crookedness of the treacherous will destroy them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16693F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16693F\"></sup>Riches do not profit in the day of wrath,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16693G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16693G\"></sup>righteousness delivers from death.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16694H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16694H\"></sup>righteousness of the blameless will smooth his way,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16694I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16694I\"></sup>the wicked will fall by his own wickedness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The righteousness of the upright will deliver them,But the treacherous will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16695J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16695J\"></sup>be caught by <i>their own</i> greed.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When a wicked man dies, <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16696K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16696K\"></sup>expectation will perish,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16696L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16696L\"></sup>hope of strong men perishes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The righteous is delivered from trouble,But the wicked takes his place.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>With <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16698M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16698M\"></sup>mouth the godless man destroys his neighbor,But through knowledge the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16698N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16698N\"></sup>righteous will be delivered.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16699O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16699O\"></sup>goes well with the righteous, the city rejoices,And when the wicked perish, there is joyful shouting.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>By the blessing of the upright a city is exalted,But by the mouth of the wicked it is torn down.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He who despises his neighbor lacks sense,But a man of understanding keeps silent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16702P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16702P\"></sup>who goes about as a talebearer reveals secrets,But he who is trustworthy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16702Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16702Q\"></sup>conceals a matter.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Where there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16703R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16703R\"></sup>guidance the people fall,But in abundance of counselors there is victory.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16704S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16704S\"></sup>guarantor for a stranger will surely suffer for it,But he who hates being a guarantor is secure.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16705T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16705T\"></sup>gracious woman attains honor,And ruthless men attain riches.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16706U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16706U\"></sup>merciful man does himself good,But the cruel man does himself harm.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wicked earns deceptive wages,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16707V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16707V\"></sup>sows righteousness <i>gets</i> a true reward.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He who is steadfast in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16708W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16708W\"></sup>righteousness <i>will attain</i> to life,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16708X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16708X\"></sup>he who pursues evil <i>will bring about</i> his own death.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The perverse in heart are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16709Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16709Y\"></sup>blameless in <i>their</i> walk are His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16709Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16709Z\"></sup>delight.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Assuredly, the evil man will not go unpunished,But the descendants of the righteous will be delivered.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><i>As</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16711AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16711AA\"></sup>ring of gold in a swine’s snout<i>So is</i> a beautiful woman who lacks discretion.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The desire of the righteous is only good,<i>But</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16712AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16712AB\"></sup>expectation of the wicked is wrath.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>There is one who scatters, and <i>yet</i> increases all the more,And there is one who withholds what is justly due, <i>and yet it results</i> only in want.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16714AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16714AC\"></sup>generous man will be prosperous,And he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16714AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16714AD\"></sup>waters will himself be watered.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He who withholds grain, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16715AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16715AE\"></sup>people will curse him,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16715AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16715AF\"></sup>blessing will be on the head of him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16715AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16715AG\"></sup>sells <i>it</i>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He who diligently seeks good seeks favor,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16716AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16716AH\"></sup>he who seeks evil, evil will come to him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16717AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16717AI\"></sup>trusts in his riches will fall,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16717AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16717AJ\"></sup>the righteous will flourish like the <i>green</i> leaf.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16718AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16718AK\"></sup>troubles his own house will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16718AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16718AL\"></sup>inherit wind,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16718AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16718AM\"></sup>the foolish will be servant to the wisehearted.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The fruit of the righteous is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16719AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16719AN\"></sup>a tree of life,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16719AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16719AO\"></sup>he who is wise wins souls.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16720AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16720AP\"></sup>the righteous will be rewarded in the earth,How much more the wicked and the sinner!"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Whoever loves discipline loves knowledge,But he who hates reproof is stupid.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16722A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16722A\"></sup>good man will obtain favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But He will condemn a man who devises evil.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16723B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16723B\"></sup>not be established by wickedness,But the root of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16723C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16723C\"></sup>righteous will not be moved.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16724D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16724D\"></sup>excellent wife is the crown of her husband,But she who shames <i>him</i> is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16724E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16724E\"></sup>rottenness in his bones.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The thoughts of the righteous are just,<i>But</i> the counsels of the wicked are deceitful.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16726F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16726F\"></sup>words of the wicked lie in wait for blood,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16726G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16726G\"></sup>mouth of the upright will deliver them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16727H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16727H\"></sup>wicked are overthrown and are no more,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16727I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16727I\"></sup>house of the righteous will stand.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A man will be praised according to his insight,But one of perverse mind will be despised.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better is he who is lightly esteemed and has a servantThan he who honors himself and lacks bread.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16730J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16730J\"></sup>righteous man has regard for the life of his animal,But <i>even</i> the compassion of the wicked is cruel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16731K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16731K\"></sup>who tills his land will have plenty of bread,But he who pursues worthless <i>things</i> lacks sense.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16732L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16732L\"></sup>wicked man desires the booty of evil men,But the root of the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16732M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16732M\"></sup>yields <i>fruit</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>An evil man is ensnared by the transgression of his lips,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16733N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16733N\"></sup>righteous will escape from trouble.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A man will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16734O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16734O\"></sup>satisfied with good by the fruit of his words,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16734P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16734P\"></sup>deeds of a man’s hands will return to him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16735Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16735Q\"></sup>way of a fool is right in his own eyes,But a wise man is he who listens to counsel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16736R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16736R\"></sup>fool’s anger is known at once,But a prudent man conceals dishonor.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He who speaks truth tells what is right,But a false witness, deceit.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16738S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16738S\"></sup>speaks rashly like the thrusts of a sword,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16738T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16738T\"></sup>tongue of the wise brings healing.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Truthful lips will be established forever,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16739U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16739U\"></sup>lying tongue is only for a moment.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Deceit is in the heart of those who devise evil,But counselors of peace have joy.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16741V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16741V\"></sup>No harm befalls the righteous,But the wicked are filled with trouble.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16742W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16742W\"></sup>Lying lips are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But those who deal faithfully are His delight.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16743X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16743X\"></sup>prudent man conceals knowledge,But the heart of fools proclaims folly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The hand of the diligent will rule,But the slack <i>hand</i> will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16744Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16744Y\"></sup>put to forced labor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16745Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16745Z\"></sup>Anxiety in a man’s heart weighs it down,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16745AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16745AA\"></sup>good word makes it glad.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The righteous is a guide to his neighbor,But the way of the wicked leads them astray.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>A lazy man does not roast his prey,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16747AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16747AB\"></sup>precious possession of a man <i>is</i> diligence.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16748AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16748AC\"></sup>In the way of righteousness is life,And in <i>its</i> pathway there is no death."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16749A\"></sup>wise son <i>accepts his</i> father’s discipline,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16749B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16749B\"></sup>scoffer does not listen to rebuke.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>From the fruit of a man’s mouth he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16750C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16750C\"></sup>enjoys good,But the desire of the treacherous is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16750D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16750D\"></sup>violence.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16751E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16751E\"></sup>guards his mouth preserves his life;The one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16751F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16751F\"></sup>opens wide his lips comes to ruin.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The soul of the sluggard craves and <i>gets</i> nothing,But the soul of the diligent is made fat.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A righteous man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16753G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16753G\"></sup>hates falsehood,But a wicked man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16753H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16753H\"></sup>acts disgustingly and shamefully.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Righteousness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16754I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16754I\"></sup>guards the one whose way is blameless,But wickedness subverts the sinner.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There is one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16755J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16755J\"></sup>pretends to be rich, but has nothing;<i>Another</i> pretends to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16755K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16755K\"></sup>poor, but has great wealth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The ransom of a man’s life is his wealth,But the poor hears no rebuke.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16757L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16757L\"></sup>light of the righteous rejoices,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16757M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16757M\"></sup>lamp of the wicked goes out.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Through insolence comes nothing but strife,But wisdom is with those who receive counsel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Wealth <i>obtained</i> by fraud dwindles,But the one who gathers by labor increases <i>it</i>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hope deferred makes the heart sick,But desire fulfilled is a tree of life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16761N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16761N\"></sup>despises the word will be in debt to it,But the one who fears the commandment will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16761O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16761O\"></sup>rewarded.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The teaching of the wise is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16762P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16762P\"></sup>fountain of life,To turn aside from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16762Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16762Q\"></sup>snares of death.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16763R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16763R\"></sup>Good understanding produces favor,But the way of the treacherous is hard.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16764S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16764S\"></sup>prudent man acts with knowledge,But a fool displays folly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A wicked messenger falls into adversity,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16765T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16765T\"></sup>a faithful envoy <i>brings</i> healing.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Poverty and shame <i>will come</i> to him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16766U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16766U\"></sup>neglects discipline,But he who regards reproof will be honored.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Desire realized is sweet to the soul,But it is an abomination to fools to turn away from evil.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16768V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16768V\"></sup>He who walks with wise men will be wise,But the companion of fools will suffer harm.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16769W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16769W\"></sup>Adversity pursues sinners,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16769X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16769X\"></sup>righteous will be rewarded with prosperity.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A good man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16770Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16770Y\"></sup>leaves an inheritance to his children’s children,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16770Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16770Z\"></sup>wealth of the sinner is stored up for the righteous.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16771AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16771AA\"></sup>Abundant food <i>is in</i> the fallow ground of the poor,But it is swept away by injustice.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16772AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16772AB\"></sup>withholds his rod hates his son,But he who loves him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16772AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16772AC\"></sup>disciplines him diligently.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16773AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16773AD\"></sup>righteous has enough to satisfy his appetite,But the stomach of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16773AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16773AE\"></sup>wicked is in need."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16774A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16774A\"></sup>wise woman builds her house,But the foolish tears it down with her own hands.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16775B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16775B\"></sup>walks in his uprightness fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16775C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16775C\"></sup>devious in his ways despises Him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the mouth of the foolish is a rod for <i>his</i> back,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16776D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16776D\"></sup>the lips of the wise will protect them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Where no oxen are, the manger is clean,But much revenue <i>comes</i> by the strength of the ox.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16778E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16778E\"></sup>trustworthy witness will not lie,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16778F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16778F\"></sup>false witness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16778G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16778G\"></sup>utters lies.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A scoffer seeks wisdom and <i>finds</i> none,But knowledge is easy to one who has understanding.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Leave the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16780H\"></sup>presence of a fool,Or you will not discern words of knowledge.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The wisdom of the sensible is to understand his way,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16781I\"></sup>the foolishness of fools is deceit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Fools mock at sin,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16782J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16782J\"></sup>among the upright there is good will.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The heart knows its own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16783K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16783K\"></sup>bitterness,And a stranger does not share its joy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16784L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16784L\"></sup>house of the wicked will be destroyed,But the tent of the upright will flourish.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16785M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16785M\"></sup>is a way <i>which seems</i> right to a man,But its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16785N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16785N\"></sup>end is the way of death.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even in laughter the heart may be in pain,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16786O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16786O\"></sup>end of joy may be grief.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The backslider in heart will have his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16787P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16787P\"></sup>fill of his own ways,But a good man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16787Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16787Q\"></sup><i>be satisfied</i> with his.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The naive believes everything,But the sensible man considers his steps.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A wise man is cautious and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16789R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16789R\"></sup>turns away from evil,But a fool is arrogant and careless.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A quick-tempered man acts foolishly,And a man of evil devices is hated.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The naive inherit foolishness,But the sensible are crowned with knowledge.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16792S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16792S\"></sup>evil will bow down before the good,And the wicked at the gates of the righteous.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16793T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16793T\"></sup>poor is hated even by his neighbor,But those who love the rich are many.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16794U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16794U\"></sup>despises his neighbor sins,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16794V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16794V\"></sup>happy is he who is gracious to the poor.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Will they not go astray who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16795W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16795W\"></sup>devise evil?But kindness and truth <i>will be to</i> those who devise good.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In all labor there is profit,But mere talk <i>leads</i> only to poverty.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16797X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16797X\"></sup>crown of the wise is their riches,<i>But</i> the folly of fools is foolishness.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A truthful witness saves lives,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16798Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16798Y\"></sup>utters lies is treacherous.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16799Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16799Z\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> there is strong confidence,And his children will have refuge.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a fountain of life,That one may avoid the snares of death.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In a multitude of people is a king’s glory,But in the dearth of people is a prince’s ruin.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16802AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16802AA\"></sup>slow to anger has great understanding,But he who is quick-tempered exalts folly.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16803AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16803AB\"></sup>tranquil heart is life to the body,But passion is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16803AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16803AC\"></sup>rottenness to the bones.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16804AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16804AD\"></sup>who oppresses the poor taunts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16804AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16804AE\"></sup>his Maker,But he who is gracious to the needy honors Him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The wicked is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16805AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16805AF\"></sup>thrust down by his wrongdoing,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16805AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16805AG\"></sup>righteous has a refuge when he dies.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Wisdom rests in the heart of one who has understanding,But in the hearts of fools it is made known.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Righteousness exalts a nation,But sin is a disgrace to <i>any</i> people.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The king’s favor is toward a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16808AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16808AH\"></sup>servant who acts wisely,But his anger is toward him who acts shamefully."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16809A\"></sup>gentle answer turns away wrath,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16809B\"></sup>harsh word stirs up anger.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16810C\"></sup>tongue of the wise makes knowledge acceptable,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16810D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16810D\"></sup>mouth of fools spouts folly.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16811E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16811E\"></sup>eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are in every place,Watching the evil and the good.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A soothing tongue is a tree of life,But perversion in it crushes the spirit.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A fool rejects his father’s discipline,But he who regards reproof is sensible.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Great wealth is <i>in</i> the house of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16814F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16814F\"></sup>righteous,But trouble is in the income of the wicked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The lips of the wise spread knowledge,But the hearts of fools are not so.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16816G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16816G\"></sup>sacrifice of the wicked is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16816H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16816H\"></sup>the prayer of the upright is His delight.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The way of the wicked is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But He loves one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16817I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16817I\"></sup>pursues righteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Grievous punishment is for him who forsakes the way;He who hates reproof will die.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16819J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16819J\"></sup>Sheol and Abaddon <i>lie open</i> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,How much more the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16819K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16819K\"></sup>hearts of men!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16820L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16820L\"></sup>scoffer does not love one who reproves him,He will not go to the wise.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16821M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16821M\"></sup>joyful heart makes a cheerful face,But when the heart is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16821N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16821N\"></sup>sad, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16821O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16821O\"></sup>spirit is broken.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16822P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16822P\"></sup>mind of the intelligent seeks knowledge,But the mouth of fools feeds on folly.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All the days of the afflicted are bad,But a cheerful heart <i>has</i> a continual feast.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16824Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16824Q\"></sup>Better is a little with the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Than great treasure and turmoil with it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16825R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16825R\"></sup>Better is a dish of vegetables where love isThan a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16825S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16825S\"></sup>fattened ox <i>served</i> with hatred.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16826T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16826T\"></sup>hot-tempered man stirs up strife,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16826U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16826U\"></sup>slow to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16826V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16826V\"></sup>calms a dispute.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The way of the lazy is as a hedge of thorns,But the path of the upright is a highway.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16828W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16828W\"></sup>wise son makes a father glad,But a foolish man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16828X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16828X\"></sup>despises his mother.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Folly is joy to him who lacks sense,But a man of understanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16829Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16829Y\"></sup>walks straight.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Without consultation, plans are frustrated,But with many counselors they succeed.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16831Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16831Z\"></sup>man has joy in an apt answer,And how delightful is a timely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16831AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16831AA\"></sup>word!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16832AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16832AB\"></sup>path of life <i>leads</i> upward for the wiseThat he may keep away from Sheol below.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16833AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16833AC\"></sup>tear down the house of the proud,But He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16833AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16833AD\"></sup>establish the boundary of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16833AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16833AE\"></sup>widow.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Evil plans are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But pleasant words are pure.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16835AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16835AF\"></sup>profits illicitly troubles his own house,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16835AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16835AG\"></sup>hates bribes will live.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The heart of the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16836AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16836AH\"></sup>ponders how to answer,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16836AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16836AI\"></sup>mouth of the wicked pours out evil things.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16837AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16837AJ\"></sup>far from the wicked,But He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16837AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16837AK\"></sup>hears the prayer of the righteous.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Bright eyes gladden the heart;Good news puts fat on the bones.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He whose ear listens to the life-giving reproofWill dwell among the wise.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16840AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16840AL\"></sup>neglects discipline <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16840AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16840AM\"></sup>despises himself,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16840AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16840AN\"></sup>listens to reproof acquires understanding.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the instruction for wisdom,And before honor <i>comes</i> humility."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16842A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16842A\"></sup>plans of the heart belong to man,But the answer of the tongue is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>All the ways of a man are clean in his own sight,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16843B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16843B\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> weighs the motives.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16844C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16844C\"></sup>Commit your works to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And your plans will be established.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16845D\"></sup>has made everything for its own purpose,Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16845E\"></sup>wicked for the day of evil.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Everyone who is proud in heart is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;Assuredly, he will not be unpunished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16847F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16847F\"></sup>lovingkindness and truth iniquity is atoned for,And by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16847G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16847G\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> one keeps away from evil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When a man’s ways are pleasing to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16848H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16848H\"></sup>makes even his enemies to be at peace with him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Better is a little with righteousnessThan great income with injustice.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The mind of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16850I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16850I\"></sup>man plans his way,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16850J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16850J\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> directs his steps.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A divine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16851K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16851K\"></sup>decision is in the lips of the king;His mouth should not err in judgment.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16852L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16852L\"></sup>just balance and scales belong to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;All the weights of the bag are His concern.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is an abomination for kings to commit wicked acts,For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16853M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16853M\"></sup>throne is established on righteousness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Righteous lips are the delight of kings,And he who speaks right is loved.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The fury of a king is <i>like</i> messengers of death,But a wise man will appease it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In the light of a king’s face is life,And his favor is like a cloud with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16856N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16856N\"></sup>spring rain.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>How much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16857O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16857O\"></sup>better it is to get wisdom than gold!And to get understanding is to be chosen above silver.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16858P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16858P\"></sup>highway of the upright is to depart from evil;He who watches his way preserves his life.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16859Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16859Q\"></sup>Pride <i>goes</i> before destruction,And a haughty spirit before stumbling.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It is better to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16860R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16860R\"></sup>humble in spirit with the lowlyThan to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16860S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16860S\"></sup>divide the spoil with the proud.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who gives attention to the word will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16861T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16861T\"></sup>find good,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16861U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16861U\"></sup>blessed is he who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16862V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16862V\"></sup>wise in heart will be called understanding,And sweetness of speech <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16862W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16862W\"></sup>increases persuasiveness.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Understanding is a fountain of life to one who has it,But the discipline of fools is folly.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16864X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16864X\"></sup>heart of the wise instructs his mouthAnd adds persuasiveness to his lips.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16865Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16865Y\"></sup>Pleasant words are a honeycomb,Sweet to the soul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16865Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16865Z\"></sup>healing to the bones.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16866AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16866AA\"></sup>There is a way <i>which seems</i> right to a man,But its end is the way of death.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>A worker’s appetite works for him,For his hunger urges him <i>on</i>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16868AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16868AB\"></sup>worthless man digs up evil,While his words are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16868AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16868AC\"></sup>scorching fire.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A perverse man spreads strife,And a slanderer separates intimate friends.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A man of violence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16870AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16870AD\"></sup>entices his neighborAnd leads him in a way that is not good.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He who winks his eyes <i>does so</i> to devise perverse things;He who compresses his lips brings evil to pass.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16872AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16872AE\"></sup>gray head is a crown of glory;It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16872AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16872AF\"></sup>is found in the way of righteousness.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He who is slow to anger is better than the mighty,And he who rules his spirit, than he who captures a city.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16874AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16874AG\"></sup>lot is cast into the lap,But its every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16874AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16874AH\"></sup>decision is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16875A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16875A\"></sup>Better is a dry morsel and quietness with itThan a house full of feasting with strife.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A servant who acts wisely will rule over a son who acts shamefully,And will share in the inheritance among brothers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16877B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16877B\"></sup>refining pot is for silver and the furnace for gold,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16877C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16877C\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> tests hearts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16878D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16878D\"></sup>evildoer listens to wicked lips;A liar pays attention to a destructive tongue.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who mocks the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16879E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16879E\"></sup>poor taunts his Maker;He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16879F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16879F\"></sup>rejoices at calamity will not go unpunished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16880G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16880G\"></sup>Grandchildren are the crown of old men,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16880H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16880H\"></sup>glory of sons is their fathers.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16881I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16881I\"></sup>Excellent speech is not fitting for a fool,Much less are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16881J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16881J\"></sup>lying lips to a prince.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16882K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16882K\"></sup>bribe is a charm in the sight of its owner;Wherever he turns, he prospers.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16883L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16883L\"></sup>conceals a transgression seeks love,But he who repeats a matter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16883M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16883M\"></sup>separates intimate friends.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A rebuke goes deeper into one who has understandingThan a hundred blows into a fool.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A rebellious man seeks only evil,So a cruel messenger will be sent against him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16886N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16886N\"></sup>man meet a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16886O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16886O\"></sup>bear robbed of her cubs,Rather than a fool in his folly.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16887P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16887P\"></sup>returns evil for good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16887Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16887Q\"></sup>Evil will not depart from his house.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The beginning of strife is <i>like</i> letting out water,So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16888R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16888R\"></sup>abandon the quarrel before it breaks out.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16889S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16889S\"></sup>justifies the wicked and he who condemns the righteous,Both of them alike are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Why is there a price in the hand of a fool to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16890T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16890T\"></sup>buy wisdom,When he has no sense?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16891U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16891U\"></sup>friend loves at all times,And a brother is born for adversity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A man lacking in sense <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16892V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16892V\"></sup>pledgesAnd becomes guarantor in the presence of his neighbor.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16893W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16893W\"></sup>loves transgression loves strife;He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16893X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16893X\"></sup>raises his door seeks destruction.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who has a crooked mind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16894Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16894Y\"></sup>finds no good,And he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16894Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16894Z\"></sup>perverted in his language falls into evil.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16895AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16895AA\"></sup>sires a fool <i>does so</i> to his sorrow,And the father of a fool has no joy.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16896AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16896AB\"></sup>joyful heart is good medicine,But a broken spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16896AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16896AC\"></sup>dries up the bones.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A wicked man receives a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16897AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16897AD\"></sup>bribe from the bosomTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16897AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16897AE\"></sup>pervert the ways of justice.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Wisdom is in the presence of the one who has understanding,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16898AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16898AF\"></sup>eyes of a fool are on the ends of the earth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16899AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16899AG\"></sup>foolish son is a grief to his fatherAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16899AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16899AH\"></sup>bitterness to her who bore him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>It is also not good to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16900AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16900AI\"></sup>fine the righteous,<i>Nor</i> to strike the noble for <i>their</i> uprightness.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16901AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16901AJ\"></sup>restrains his words has knowledge,And he who has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16901AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16901AK\"></sup>cool spirit is a man of understanding.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Even a fool, when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16902AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16902AL\"></sup>keeps silent, is considered wise;When he closes his lips, he is <i>considered</i> prudent."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>He who separates himself seeks <i>his own</i> desire,He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16903A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16903A\"></sup>quarrels against all sound wisdom.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A fool does not delight in understanding,But only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16904B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16904B\"></sup>in revealing his own mind.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When a wicked man comes, contempt also comes,And with dishonor <i>comes</i> scorn.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The words of a man’s mouth are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16906C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16906C\"></sup>deep waters;The fountain of wisdom is a bubbling brook.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16907D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16907D\"></sup>show partiality to the wicked is not good,<i>Nor</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16907E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16907E\"></sup>thrust aside the righteous in judgment.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A fool’s lips bring strife,And his mouth calls for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16908F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16908F\"></sup>blows.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16909G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16909G\"></sup>fool’s mouth is his ruin,And his lips are the snare of his soul.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The words of a whisperer are like dainty morsels,And they go down into the innermost parts of the body.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He also who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16911H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16911H\"></sup>slack in his work<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16911I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16911I\"></sup>Is brother to him who destroys.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16912J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16912J\"></sup>name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16912K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16912K\"></sup>strong tower;The righteous runs into it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16912L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16912L\"></sup>is safe.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16913M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16913M\"></sup>rich man’s wealth is his strong city,And like a high wall in his own imagination.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16914N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16914N\"></sup>Before destruction the heart of man is haughty,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16914O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16914O\"></sup>humility <i>goes</i> before honor.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16915P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16915P\"></sup>gives an answer before he hears,It is folly and shame to him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16916Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16916Q\"></sup>spirit of a man can endure his sickness,But <i>as for</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16916R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16916R\"></sup>broken spirit who can bear it?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16917S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16917S\"></sup>mind of the prudent acquires knowledge,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16917T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16917T\"></sup>ear of the wise seeks knowledge.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A man’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16918U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16918U\"></sup>gift makes room for himAnd brings him before great men.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The first to plead his case <i>seems</i> right,<i>Until</i> another comes and examines him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The <i>cast</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16920V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16920V\"></sup>lot puts an end to strifeAnd decides between the mighty ones.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A brother offended <i>is harder to be won</i> than a strong city,And contentions are like the bars of a citadel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>With the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16922W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16922W\"></sup>fruit of a man’s mouth his stomach will be satisfied;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16922X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16922X\"></sup>He will be satisfied <i>with</i> the product of his lips.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16923Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16923Y\"></sup>Death and life are in the power of the tongue,And those who love it will eat its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16923Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16923Z\"></sup>fruit.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He who finds a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16924AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16924AA\"></sup>wife finds a good thingAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16924AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16924AB\"></sup>obtains favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16925AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16925AC\"></sup>poor man utters supplications,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16925AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16925AD\"></sup>rich man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16925AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16925AE\"></sup>answers roughly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A man of <i>too many</i> friends <i>comes</i> to ruin,But there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16926AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16926AF\"></sup>a friend who sticks closer than a brother."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16927A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16927A\"></sup>Better is a poor man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16927B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16927B\"></sup>walks in his integrityThan he who is perverse in speech and is a fool.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Also it is not good for a person to be without knowledge,And he who hurries <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16928C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16928C\"></sup>his footsteps errs.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16929D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16929D\"></sup>foolishness of man ruins his way,And his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16929E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16929E\"></sup>rages against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16930F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16930F\"></sup>Wealth adds many friends,But a poor man is separated from his friend.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16931G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16931G\"></sup>false witness will not go unpunished,And he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16931H\"></sup>tells lies will not escape.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16932I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16932I\"></sup>Many will seek the favor of a generous man,And every man is a friend to him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16932J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16932J\"></sup>gives gifts.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All the brothers of a poor man hate him;How much more do his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16933K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16933K\"></sup>friends abandon him!He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16933L\"></sup>pursues <i>them with</i> words, <i>but</i> they are gone.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who gets wisdom loves his own soul;He who keeps understanding will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16934M\"></sup>find good.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16935N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16935N\"></sup>false witness will not go unpunished,And he who tells lies will perish.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Luxury is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16936O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16936O\"></sup>not fitting for a fool;Much less for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16936P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16936P\"></sup>slave to rule over princes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A man’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16937Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16937Q\"></sup>discretion makes him slow to anger,And it is his glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16937R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16937R\"></sup>to overlook a transgression.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16938S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16938S\"></sup>king’s wrath is like the roaring of a lion,But his favor is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16938T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16938T\"></sup>dew on the grass.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16939U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16939U\"></sup>foolish son is destruction to his father,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16939V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16939V\"></sup>contentions of a wife are a constant dripping.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>House and wealth are an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16940W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16940W\"></sup>inheritance from fathers,But a prudent wife is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16941X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16941X\"></sup>Laziness casts into a deep sleep,And an idle man will suffer hunger.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16942Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16942Y\"></sup>keeps the commandment keeps his soul,<i>But</i> he who is careless of conduct will die.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>One who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16943Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16943Z\"></sup>is gracious to a poor man lends to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And He will repay him for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16943AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16943AA\"></sup>good deed.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16944AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16944AB\"></sup>Discipline your son while there is hope,And do not desire his death.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>A man of</i> great anger will bear the penalty,For if you rescue <i>him</i>, you will only have to do it again.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16946AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16946AC\"></sup>Listen to counsel and accept discipline,That you may be wise the rest of your days.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16947AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16947AD\"></sup>plans are in a man’s heart,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16947AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16947AE\"></sup>counsel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will stand.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What is desirable in a man is his kindness,And <i>it is</i> better to be a poor man than a liar.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16949AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16949AF\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>leads</i> to life,So that one may sleep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16949AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16949AG\"></sup>satisfied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16949AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16949AH\"></sup>untouched by evil.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16950AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16950AI\"></sup>sluggard buries his hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16950AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16950AJ\"></sup>in the dish,<i>But</i> will not even bring it back to his mouth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16951AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16951AK\"></sup>Strike a scoffer and the naive may become shrewd,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16951AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16951AL\"></sup>reprove one who has understanding and he will gain knowledge.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16952AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16952AM\"></sup>who assaults <i>his</i> father <i>and</i> drives <i>his</i> mother awayIs a shameful and disgraceful son.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Cease listening, my son, to discipline,<i>And you will</i> stray from the words of knowledge.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A rascally witness makes a mockery of justice,And the mouth of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16954AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16954AN\"></sup>spreads iniquity.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Judgments are prepared for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16955AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16955AO\"></sup>scoffers,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16955AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16955AP\"></sup>blows for the back of fools."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16956A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16956A\"></sup>Wine is a mocker, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16956B\"></sup>strong drink a brawler,And whoever is intoxicated by it is not wise.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The terror of a king is like the growling of a lion;He who provokes him to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16957C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16957C\"></sup>forfeits his own life.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16958D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16958D\"></sup>Keeping away from strife is an honor for a man,But any fool will quarrel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16959E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16959E\"></sup>sluggard does not plow after the autumn,So he begs during the harvest and has nothing.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A plan in the heart of a man is <i>like</i> deep water,But a man of understanding draws it out.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16961F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16961F\"></sup>proclaims his own loyalty,But who can find a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16961G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16961G\"></sup>trustworthy man?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A righteous man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16962H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16962H\"></sup>walks in his integrity—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16962I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16962I\"></sup>How blessed are his sons after him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16963J\"></sup>A king who sits on the throne of justiceDisperses all evil with his eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16964K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16964K\"></sup>Who can say, “I have cleansed my heart,I am pure from my sin”?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16965L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16965L\"></sup>Differing weights and differing measures,Both of them are abominable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It is by his deeds that a lad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16966M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16966M\"></sup>distinguishes himselfIf his conduct is pure and right.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The hearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16967N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16967N\"></sup>ear and the seeing eye,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made both of them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16968O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16968O\"></sup>Do not love sleep, or you will become poor;Open your eyes, <i>and</i> you will be satisfied with food.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Bad, bad,” says the buyer,But when he goes his way, then he boasts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There is gold, and an abundance of jewels;But the lips of knowledge are a more precious thing.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Take his garment when he becomes surety for a stranger;And for foreigners, hold him in pledge.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16972P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16972P\"></sup>Bread obtained by falsehood is sweet to a man,But afterward his mouth will be filled with gravel.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Prepare <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16973Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16973Q\"></sup>plans by consultation,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16973R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16973R\"></sup>make war by wise guidance.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16974S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16974S\"></sup>goes about as a slanderer reveals secrets,Therefore do not associate with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16974T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16974T\"></sup>a gossip.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16975U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16975U\"></sup>curses his father or his mother,His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16975V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16975V\"></sup>lamp will go out in time of darkness.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>An inheritance gained hurriedly at the beginningWill not be blessed in the end.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16977W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16977W\"></sup>Do not say, “I will repay evil”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16977X\"></sup>Wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and He will save you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16978Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16978Y\"></sup>Differing weights are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16978Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16978Z\"></sup>false scale is not good.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16979AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16979AA\"></sup>Man’s steps are <i>ordained</i> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,How then can man understand his way?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is a trap for a man to say rashly, “It is holy!”And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16980AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16980AB\"></sup>after the vows to make inquiry.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16981AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16981AC\"></sup>wise king winnows the wicked,And drives the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16981AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16981AD\"></sup><i>threshing</i> wheel over them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16982AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16982AE\"></sup>spirit of man is the lamp of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Searching all the innermost parts of his being.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Loyalty and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16983AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16983AF\"></sup>truth preserve the king,And he upholds his throne by righteousness.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The glory of young men is their strength,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16984AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16984AG\"></sup>honor of old men is their gray hair.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16985AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16985AH\"></sup>Stripes that wound scour away evil,And strokes <i>reach</i> the innermost parts."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The king’s heart is <i>like</i> channels of water in the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16986A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16986A\"></sup>turns it wherever He wishes.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16987B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16987B\"></sup>Every man’s way is right in his own eyes,But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16987C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16987C\"></sup>weighs the hearts.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16988D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16988D\"></sup>righteousness and justiceIs desired by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> more than sacrifice.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Haughty eyes and a proud heart,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16989E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16989E\"></sup>lamp of the wicked, is sin.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The plans of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16990F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16990F\"></sup>diligent <i>lead</i> surely to advantage,But everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16990G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16990G\"></sup>who is hasty <i>comes</i> surely to poverty.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16991H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16991H\"></sup>acquisition of treasures by a lying tongueIs a fleeting vapor, the pursuit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16991I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16991I\"></sup>death.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The violence of the wicked will drag them away,Because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16992J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16992J\"></sup>refuse to act with justice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The way of a guilty man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16993K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16993K\"></sup>crooked,But as for the pure, his conduct is upright.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It is better to live in a corner of a roofThan in a house shared with a contentious woman.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The soul of the wicked desires evil;His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16995L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16995L\"></sup>neighbor finds no favor in his eyes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16996M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16996M\"></sup>scoffer is punished, the naive becomes wise;But when the wise is instructed, he receives knowledge.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The righteous one considers the house of the wicked,Turning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16997N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16997N\"></sup>wicked to ruin.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16998O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16998O\"></sup>shuts his ear to the cry of the poorWill also cry himself and not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16998P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16998P\"></sup>answered.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-16999Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-16999Q\"></sup>gift in secret subdues anger,And a bribe in the bosom, strong wrath.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The exercise of justice is joy for the righteous,But is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17000R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17000R\"></sup>terror to the workers of iniquity.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A man who wanders from the way of understandingWill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17001S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17001S\"></sup>rest in the assembly of the dead.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17002T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17002T\"></sup>loves pleasure <i>will become</i> a poor man;He who loves wine and oil will not become rich.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wicked is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17003U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17003U\"></sup>ransom for the righteous,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17003V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17003V\"></sup>treacherous is in the place of the upright.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17004W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17004W\"></sup>It is better to live in a desert landThan with a contentious and vexing woman.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>There is precious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17005X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17005X\"></sup>treasure and oil in the dwelling of the wise,But a foolish man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17005Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17005Y\"></sup>swallows it up.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17006Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17006Z\"></sup>pursues righteousness and loyaltyFinds life, righteousness and honor.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17007AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17007AA\"></sup>wise man scales the city of the mightyAnd brings down the stronghold in which they trust.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17008AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17008AB\"></sup>guards his mouth and his tongue,Guards his soul from troubles.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Proud,” “Haughty,” “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17009AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17009AC\"></sup>Scoffer,” are his names,Who acts with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17009AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17009AD\"></sup>insolent pride.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17010AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17010AE\"></sup>desire of the sluggard puts him to death,For his hands refuse to work;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>All day long he is craving,While the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17011AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17011AF\"></sup>gives and does not hold back.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17012AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17012AG\"></sup>sacrifice of the wicked is an abomination,How much more when he brings it with evil intent!",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17013AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17013AH\"></sup>false witness will perish,But the man who listens <i>to the truth</i> will speak forever.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A wicked man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17014AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17014AI\"></sup>displays a bold face,But as for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17014AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17014AJ\"></sup>upright, he makes his way sure.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17015AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17015AK\"></sup>no wisdom and no understandingAnd no counsel against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17016AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17016AL\"></sup>horse is prepared for the day of battle,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17016AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17016AM\"></sup>victory belongs to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17017A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17017A\"></sup><i>good</i> name is to be more desired than great wealth,Favor is better than silver and gold.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The rich and the poor have a common bond,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17018B\"></sup>maker of them all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17019C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17019C\"></sup>prudent sees the evil and hides himself,But the naive go on, and are punished for it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The reward of humility <i>and</i> the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Are riches, honor and life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17021D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17021D\"></sup>Thorns <i>and</i> snares are in the way of the perverse;He who guards himself will be far from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17022E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17022E\"></sup>Train up a child in the way he should go,Even when he is old he will not depart from it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17023F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17023F\"></sup>rich rules over the poor,And the borrower <i>becomes</i> the lender’s slave.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17024G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17024G\"></sup>sows iniquity will reap vanity,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17024H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17024H\"></sup>rod of his fury will perish.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17025I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17025I\"></sup>generous will be blessed,For he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17025J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17025J\"></sup>gives some of his food to the poor.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17026K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17026K\"></sup>Drive out the scoffer, and contention will go out,Even strife and dishonor will cease.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He who loves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17027L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17027L\"></sup>purity of heart<i>And</i> whose speech is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17027M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17027M\"></sup>gracious, the king is his friend.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> preserve knowledge,But He overthrows the words of the treacherous man.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17029N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17029N\"></sup>sluggard says, “There is a lion outside;I will be killed in the streets!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17030O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17030O\"></sup>an adulteress is a deep pit;He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17030P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17030P\"></sup>cursed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will fall into it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Foolishness is bound up in the heart of a child;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17031Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17031Q\"></sup>rod of discipline will remove it far from him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17032R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17032R\"></sup>who oppresses the poor to make more for himselfOr who gives to the rich, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17032S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17032S\"></sup><i>will</i> only <i>come to</i> poverty.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17033T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17033T\"></sup>Incline your ear and hear the words of the wise,And apply your mind to my knowledge;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17034U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17034U\"></sup>pleasant if you keep them within you,That they may be ready on your lips.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17035V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17035V\"></sup>trust may be in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,I have taught you today, even you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Have I not written to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17036W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17036W\"></sup>excellent thingsOf counsels and knowledge,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17037X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17037X\"></sup>know the certainty of the words of truthThat you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17037Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17037Y\"></sup>correctly answer him who sent you?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17038Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17038Z\"></sup>Do not rob the poor because he is poor,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17038AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17038AA\"></sup>crush the afflicted at the gate;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17039AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17039AB\"></sup>plead their caseAnd take the life of those who rob them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Do not associate with a man <i>given</i> to anger;Or go with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17040AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17040AC\"></sup>hot-tempered man,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Or you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17041AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17041AD\"></sup>learn his waysAnd find a snare for yourself.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do not be among those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17042AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17042AE\"></sup>give pledges,Among those who become guarantors for debts.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If you have nothing with which to pay,Why should he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17043AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17043AF\"></sup>take your bed from under you?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17044AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17044AG\"></sup>Do not move the ancient boundaryWhich your fathers have set.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do you see a man skilled in his work?He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17045AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17045AH\"></sup>stand before kings;He will not stand before obscure men."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>When you sit down to dine with a ruler,Consider carefully what is before you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And put a knife to your throatIf you are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17047A\"></sup>man of <i>great</i> appetite.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17048B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17048B\"></sup>desire his delicacies,For it is deceptive food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17049C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17049C\"></sup>Do not weary yourself to gain wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17049D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17049D\"></sup>Cease from your consideration <i>of it</i>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When you set your eyes on it, it is gone.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17050E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17050E\"></sup><i>wealth</i> certainly makes itself wingsLike an eagle that flies <i>toward</i> the heavens.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17051F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17051F\"></sup>Do not eat the bread of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17051G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17051G\"></sup>selfish man,Or desire his delicacies;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For as he thinks within himself, so he is.He says to you, “Eat and drink!”But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17052H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17052H\"></sup>his heart is not with you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17053I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17053I\"></sup>vomit up the morsel you have eaten,And waste your compliments.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17054J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17054J\"></sup>Do not speak in the hearing of a fool,For he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17054K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17054K\"></sup>despise the wisdom of your words.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not move the ancient boundaryOr <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17055L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17055L\"></sup>go into the fields of the fatherless,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17056M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17056M\"></sup>Redeemer is strong;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17056N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17056N\"></sup>He will plead their case against you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Apply your heart to disciplineAnd your ears to words of knowledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17058O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17058O\"></sup>Do not hold back discipline from the child,Although you strike him with the rod, he will not die.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You shall strike him with the rodAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17059P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17059P\"></sup>rescue his soul from Sheol.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>My son, if your heart is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17060Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17060Q\"></sup>wise,My own heart also will be glad;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And my inmost being will rejoiceWhen your lips speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17061R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17061R\"></sup>what is right.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17062S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17062S\"></sup>Do not let your heart envy sinners,But <i>live</i> in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17062T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17062T\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> always.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Surely there is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17063U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17063U\"></sup>future,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17063V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17063V\"></sup>hope will not be cut off.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Listen, my son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17064W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17064W\"></sup>be wise,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17064X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17064X\"></sup>direct your heart in the way.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do not be with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17065Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17065Y\"></sup>heavy drinkers of wine,<i>Or</i> with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17065Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17065Z\"></sup>gluttonous eaters of meat;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17066AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17066AA\"></sup>heavy drinker and the glutton will come to poverty,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17066AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17066AB\"></sup>drowsiness will clothe <i>one</i> with rags.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17067AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17067AC\"></sup>Listen to your father who begot you,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17067AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17067AD\"></sup>do not despise your mother when she is old.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17068AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17068AE\"></sup>Buy truth, and do not sell <i>it</i>,<i>Get</i> wisdom and instruction and understanding.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The father of the righteous will greatly rejoice,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17069AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17069AF\"></sup>he who sires a wise son will be glad in him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17070AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17070AG\"></sup>father and your mother be glad,And let her rejoice who gave birth to you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17071AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17071AH\"></sup>Give me your heart, my son,And let your eyes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17071AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17071AI\"></sup>delight in my ways.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For a harlot is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17072AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17072AJ\"></sup>deep pitAnd an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17072AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17072AK\"></sup>adulterous woman is a narrow well.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Surely she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17073AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17073AL\"></sup>lurks as a robber,And increases the faithless among men.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17074AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17074AM\"></sup>woe? Who has sorrow?Who has contentions? Who has complaining?Who has wounds without cause?Who has redness of eyes?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17075AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17075AN\"></sup>linger long over wine,Those who go to taste <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17075AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17075AO\"></sup>mixed wine.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do not look on the wine when it is red,When it sparkles in the cup,When it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17076AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17076AP\"></sup>goes down smoothly;",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>At the last it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17077AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17077AQ\"></sup>bites like a serpentAnd stings like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17077AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17077AR\"></sup>viper.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Your eyes will see strange thingsAnd your mind will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17078AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17078AS\"></sup>utter perverse things.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And you will be like one who lies down in the middle of the sea,Or like one who lies down on the top of a mast.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17080AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17080AT\"></sup>struck me, <i>but</i> I did not become ill;They beat me, <i>but</i> I did not know <i>it</i>.When shall I awake?I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17080AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17080AU\"></sup>seek another drink.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>Do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17081A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17081A\"></sup>envious of evil men,Nor desire to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17081B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17081B\"></sup>be with them;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For their minds devise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17082C\"></sup>violence,And their lips <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17082D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17082D\"></sup>talk of trouble.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17083E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17083E\"></sup>By wisdom a house is built,And by understanding it is established;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And by knowledge the rooms are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17084F\"></sup>filledWith all precious and pleasant riches.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17085G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17085G\"></sup>wise man is strong,And a man of knowledge increases power.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17086H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17086H\"></sup>by wise guidance you will wage war,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17086I\"></sup>in abundance of counselors there is victory.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Wisdom is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17087J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17087J\"></sup><i>too</i> exalted for a fool,He does not open his mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17087K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17087K\"></sup>in the gate.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>One who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17088L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17088L\"></sup>plans to do evil,Men will call a schemer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17089M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17089M\"></sup>devising of folly is sin,And the scoffer is an abomination to men.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17090N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17090N\"></sup>are slack in the day of distress,Your strength is limited.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17091O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17091O\"></sup>Deliver those who are being taken away to death,And those who are staggering to slaughter, Oh hold <i>them</i> back.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you say, “See, we did not know this,”Does He not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17092P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17092P\"></sup>consider <i>it</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17092Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17092Q\"></sup>who weighs the hearts?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17092R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17092R\"></sup>does He not know <i>it</i> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17092S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17092S\"></sup>keeps your soul?And will He not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17092T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17092T\"></sup>render to man according to his work?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My son, eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17093U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17093U\"></sup>honey, for it is good,Yes, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17093V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17093V\"></sup>honey from the comb is sweet to your taste;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Know <i>that</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17094W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17094W\"></sup>wisdom is thus for your soul;If you find <i>it</i>, then there will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17094X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17094X\"></sup>future,And your hope will not be cut off.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17095Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17095Y\"></sup>Do not lie in wait, O wicked man, against the dwelling of the righteous;Do not destroy his resting place;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17096Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17096Z\"></sup>righteous man falls seven times, and rises again,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17096AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17096AA\"></sup>wicked stumble in <i>time of</i> calamity.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17097AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17097AB\"></sup>Do not rejoice when your enemy falls,And do not let your heart be glad when he stumbles;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Or the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will see <i>it</i> and be displeased,And turn His anger away from him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17099AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17099AC\"></sup>Do not fret because of evildoersOr be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17099AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17099AD\"></sup>envious of the wicked;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17100AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17100AE\"></sup>there will be no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17100AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17100AF\"></sup>future for the evil man;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17100AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17100AG\"></sup>lamp of the wicked will be put out.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17101AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17101AH\"></sup>fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the king;Do not associate with those who are given to change,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17102AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17102AI\"></sup>calamity will rise suddenly,And who knows the ruin <i>that comes</i> from both of them?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>These also are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17103AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17103AJ\"></sup>sayings of the wise.To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17103AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17103AK\"></sup>show partiality in judgment is not good.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17104AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17104AL\"></sup>who says to the wicked, “You are righteous,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17104AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17104AM\"></sup>Peoples will curse him, nations will abhor him;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17105AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17105AN\"></sup>to those who rebuke the <i>wicked</i> will be delight,And a good blessing will come upon them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He kisses the lipsWho gives a right answer.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Prepare your work outsideAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17107AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17107AO\"></sup>make it ready for yourself in the field;Afterwards, then, build your house.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17108AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17108AP\"></sup>witness against your neighbor without cause,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17108AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17108AQ\"></sup>do not deceive with your lips.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17109AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17109AR\"></sup>Do not say, “Thus I shall do to him as he has done to me;I will render to the man according to his work.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I passed by the field of the sluggardAnd by the vineyard of the man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17110AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17110AS\"></sup>lacking sense,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And behold, it was completely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17111AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17111AT\"></sup>overgrown with thistles;Its surface was covered with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17111AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17111AU\"></sup>nettles,And its stone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17111AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17111AV\"></sup>wall was broken down.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>When I saw, I reflected upon it;I looked, <i>and</i> received instruction.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17113AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17113AW\"></sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,A little folding of the hands to rest,”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then your poverty will come <i>as</i> a robberAnd your want like an armed man."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>These also are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17115A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17115A\"></sup>proverbs of Solomon which the men of Hezekiah, king of Judah, transcribed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It is the glory of God to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17116B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17116B\"></sup>conceal a matter,But the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17116C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17116C\"></sup>kings is to search out a matter.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>As</i> the heavens for height and the earth for depth,So the heart of kings is unsearchable.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Take away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17118D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17118D\"></sup>dross from the silver,And there comes out a vessel for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17118E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17118E\"></sup>smith;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Take away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17119F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17119F\"></sup>wicked before the king,And his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17119G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17119G\"></sup>throne will be established in righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not claim honor in the presence of the king,And do not stand in the place of great men;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17121H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17121H\"></sup>it is better that it be said to you, “Come up here,”Than for you to be placed lower in the presence of the prince,Whom your eyes have seen.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not go out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17122I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17122I\"></sup>hastily to argue <i>your case</i>;Otherwise, what will you do in the end,When your neighbor humiliates you?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17123J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17123J\"></sup>Argue your case with your neighbor,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17123K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17123K\"></sup>do not reveal the secret of another,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Or he who hears <i>it</i> will reproach you,And the evil report about you will not pass away.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>Like</i> apples of gold in settings of silverIs a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17125L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17125L\"></sup>word spoken in right circumstances.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>Like</i> an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17126M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17126M\"></sup>earring of gold and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17126N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17126N\"></sup>ornament of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17126O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17126O\"></sup>fine goldIs a wise reprover to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17126P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17126P\"></sup>listening ear.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Like the cold of snow in the time of harvestIs a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17127Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17127Q\"></sup>faithful messenger to those who send him,For he refreshes the soul of his masters.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><i>Like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17128R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17128R\"></sup>clouds and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17128S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17128S\"></sup>wind without rainIs a man who boasts of his gifts falsely.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17129T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17129T\"></sup>forbearance a ruler may be persuaded,And a soft tongue breaks the bone.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17130U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17130U\"></sup>found honey? Eat <i>only</i> what you need,That you not have it in excess and vomit it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let your foot rarely be in your neighbor’s house,Or he will become weary of you and hate you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>Like</i> a club and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17132V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17132V\"></sup>sword and a sharp <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17132W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17132W\"></sup>arrowIs a man who bears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17132X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17132X\"></sup>false witness against his neighbor.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>Like</i> a bad tooth and an unsteady footIs confidence in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17133Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17133Y\"></sup>faithless man in time of trouble.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><i>Like</i> one who takes off a garment on a cold day, <i>or like</i> vinegar on soda,Is he who sings songs to a troubled heart.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17135Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17135Z\"></sup>If your enemy is hungry, give him food to eat;And if he is thirsty, give him water to drink;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For you will heap burning coals on his head,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17136AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17136AA\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will reward you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The north wind brings forth rain,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17137AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17137AB\"></sup>backbiting tongue, an angry countenance.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17138AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17138AC\"></sup>better to live in a corner of the roofThan in a house shared with a contentious woman.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><i>Like</i> cold water to a weary soul,So is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17139AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17139AD\"></sup>good news from a distant land.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>Like</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17140AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17140AE\"></sup>trampled spring and a polluted wellIs a righteous man who gives way before the wicked.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>It is not good to eat much honey,Nor is it glory to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17141AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17141AF\"></sup>search out one’s own glory.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><i>Like</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17142AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17142AG\"></sup>city that is broken into <i>and</i> without wallsIs a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17142AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17142AH\"></sup>who has no control over his spirit."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Like snow in summer and like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17143A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17143A\"></sup>rain in harvest,So honor is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17143B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17143B\"></sup>fitting for a fool.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17144C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17144C\"></sup>sparrow in <i>its</i> flitting, like a swallow in <i>its</i> flying,So a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17144D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17144D\"></sup>curse without cause does not alight.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17145E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17145E\"></sup>whip is for the horse, a bridle for the donkey,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17145F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17145F\"></sup>rod for the back of fools.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17146G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17146G\"></sup>Do not answer a fool according to his folly,Or you will also be like him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17147H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17147H\"></sup>Answer a fool as his folly <i>deserves</i>,That he not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17147I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17147I\"></sup>wise in his own eyes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He cuts off <i>his own</i> feet <i>and</i> drinks violenceWho sends a message by the hand of a fool.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><i>Like</i> the legs <i>which</i> are useless to the lame,So is a proverb in the mouth of fools.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like one who binds a stone in a sling,So is he who gives honor to a fool.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><i>Like</i> a thorn <i>which</i> falls into the hand of a drunkard,So is a proverb in the mouth of fools.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><i>Like</i> an archer who wounds everyone,So is he who hires a fool or who hires those who pass by.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17153J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17153J\"></sup>a dog that returns to its vomitIs a fool who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17153K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17153K\"></sup>repeats his folly.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do you see a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17154L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17154L\"></sup>wise in his own eyes?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17154M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17154M\"></sup>There is more hope for a fool than for him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17155N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17155N\"></sup>sluggard says, “There is a lion in the road!A lion is in the open square!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><i>As</i> the door turns on its hinges,So <i>does</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17156O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17156O\"></sup>sluggard on his bed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17157P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17157P\"></sup>sluggard buries his hand in the dish;He is weary of bringing it to his mouth again.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The sluggard is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17158Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17158Q\"></sup>wiser in his own eyesThan seven men who can give a discreet answer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><i>Like</i> one who takes a dog by the earsIs he who passes by <i>and</i> meddles with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17159R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17159R\"></sup>strife not belonging to him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Like a madman who throws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17160S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17160S\"></sup>Firebrands, arrows and death,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So is the man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17161T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17161T\"></sup>deceives his neighbor,And says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17161U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17161U\"></sup>Was I not joking?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For lack of wood the fire goes out,And where there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17162V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17162V\"></sup>whisperer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17162W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17162W\"></sup>contention quiets down.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><i>Like</i> charcoal to hot embers and wood to fire,So is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17163X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17163X\"></sup>contentious man to kindle strife.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17164Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17164Y\"></sup>words of a whisperer are like dainty morsels,And they go down into the innermost parts of the body.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><i>Like</i> an earthen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17165Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17165Z\"></sup>vessel overlaid with silver <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17165AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17165AA\"></sup>drossAre burning lips and a wicked heart.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17166AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17166AB\"></sup>hates disguises <i>it</i> with his lips,But he lays up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17166AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17166AC\"></sup>deceit in his heart.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17167AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17167AD\"></sup>speaks graciously, do not believe him,For there are seven abominations in his heart.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>Though his</i> hatred <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17168AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17168AE\"></sup>covers itself with guile,His wickedness will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17168AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17168AF\"></sup>revealed before the assembly.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17169AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17169AG\"></sup>digs a pit will fall into it,And he who rolls a stone, it will come back on him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A lying tongue hates those it crushes,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17170AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17170AH\"></sup>flattering mouth works ruin."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17171A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17171A\"></sup>Do not boast about tomorrow,For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17171B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17171B\"></sup>do not know what a day may bring forth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17172C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17172C\"></sup>another praise you, and not your own mouth;A stranger, and not your own lips.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A stone is heavy and the sand weighty,But the provocation of a fool is heavier than both of them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Wrath is fierce and anger is a flood,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17174D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17174D\"></sup>who can stand before jealousy?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Better is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17175E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17175E\"></sup>open rebukeThan love that is concealed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Faithful are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17176F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17176F\"></sup>wounds of a friend,But deceitful are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17176G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17176G\"></sup>kisses of an enemy.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A sated man loathes honey,But to a famished man any bitter thing is sweet.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17178H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17178H\"></sup>bird that wanders from her nest,So is a man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17178I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17178I\"></sup>wanders from his home.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17179J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17179J\"></sup>Oil and perfume make the heart glad,So a man’s counsel is sweet to his friend.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not forsake your own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17180K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17180K\"></sup>friend or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17180L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17180L\"></sup>your father’s friend,And do not go to your brother’s house in the day of your calamity;Better is a neighbor who is near than a brother far away.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17181M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17181M\"></sup>Be wise, my son, and make my heart glad,That I may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17181N\"></sup>reply to him who reproaches me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A prudent man sees evil <i>and</i> hides himself,The naive proceed <i>and</i> pay the penalty.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17183O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17183O\"></sup>Take his garment when he becomes surety for a stranger;And for an adulterous woman hold him in pledge.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17184P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17184P\"></sup>He who blesses his friend with a loud voice early in the morning,It will be reckoned a curse to him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17185Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17185Q\"></sup>constant dripping on a day of steady rainAnd a contentious woman are alike;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He who would restrain her restrains the wind,And grasps oil with his right hand.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Iron sharpens iron,So one man sharpens another.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He who tends the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17188R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17188R\"></sup>fig tree will eat its fruit,And he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17188S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17188S\"></sup>cares for his master will be honored.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As in water face <i>reflects</i> face,So the heart of man <i>reflects</i> man.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17190T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17190T\"></sup>Sheol and Abaddon are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17190U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17190U\"></sup>never satisfied,Nor are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17190V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17190V\"></sup>eyes of man ever satisfied.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17191W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17191W\"></sup>crucible is for silver and the furnace for gold,And each <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17191X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17191X\"></sup><i>is tested</i> by the praise accorded him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Though you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17192Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17192Y\"></sup>pound a fool in a mortar with a pestle along with crushed grain,<i>Yet</i> his foolishness will not depart from him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17193Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17193Z\"></sup>Know well the condition of your flocks,<i>And</i> pay attention to your herds;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For riches are not forever,Nor does a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17194AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17194AA\"></sup>crown <i>endure</i> to all generations.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><i>When</i> the grass disappears, the new growth is seen,And the herbs of the mountains are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17195AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17195AB\"></sup>gathered in,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The lambs <i>will be</i> for your clothing,And the goats <i>will bring</i> the price of a field,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <i>there will be</i> goats’ milk enough for your food,For the food of your household,And sustenance for your maidens."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>The wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17198A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17198A\"></sup>flee when no one is pursuing,But the righteous are bold as a lion.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>By the transgression of a land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17199B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17199B\"></sup>many are its princes,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17199C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17199C\"></sup>by a man of understanding <i>and</i> knowledge, so it endures.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17200D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17200D\"></sup>poor man who oppresses the lowlyIs <i>like</i> a driving rain which leaves no food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Those who forsake the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17201E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17201E\"></sup>praise the wicked,But those who keep the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17201F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17201F\"></sup>strive with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Evil men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17202G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17202G\"></sup>do not understand justice,But those who seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17202H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17202H\"></sup>understand all things.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17203I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17203I\"></sup>Better is the poor who walks in his integrityThan he who is crooked though he be rich.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He who keeps the law is a discerning son,But he who is a companion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17204J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17204J\"></sup>gluttons humiliates his father.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who increases his wealth by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17205K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17205K\"></sup>interest and usuryGathers it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17205L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17205L\"></sup>for him who is gracious to the poor.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He who turns away his ear from listening to the law,Even his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17206M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17206M\"></sup>prayer is an abomination.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He who leads the upright astray in an evil wayWill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17207N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17207N\"></sup>himself fall into his own pit,But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17207O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17207O\"></sup>blameless will inherit good.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The rich man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17208P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17208P\"></sup>wise in his own eyes,But the poor who has understanding sees through him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17209Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17209Q\"></sup>righteous triumph, there is great glory,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17209R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17209R\"></sup>when the wicked rise, men hide themselves.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17210S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17210S\"></sup>conceals his transgressions will not prosper,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17210T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17210T\"></sup>confesses and forsakes <i>them</i> will find compassion.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>How blessed is the man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17211U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17211U\"></sup>fears always,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17211V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17211V\"></sup>hardens his heart will fall into calamity.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><i>Like</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17212W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17212W\"></sup>roaring lion and a rushing bearIs a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17212X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17212X\"></sup>wicked ruler over a poor people.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17213Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17213Y\"></sup>leader who is a great oppressor lacks understanding,<i>But</i> he who hates unjust gain will prolong <i>his</i> days.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17214Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17214Z\"></sup>laden with the guilt of human bloodWill be a fugitive until death; let no one support him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He who walks blamelessly will be delivered,But he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17215AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17215AA\"></sup>crooked will fall all at once.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17216AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17216AB\"></sup>He who tills his land will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17216AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17216AC\"></sup>have plenty of food,But he who follows empty <i>pursuits</i> will have poverty in plenty.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17217AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17217AD\"></sup>faithful man will abound with blessings,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17217AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17217AE\"></sup>makes haste to be rich will not go unpunished.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17218AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17218AF\"></sup>show partiality is not good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17218AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17218AG\"></sup>Because for a piece of bread a man will transgress.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A man with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17219AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17219AH\"></sup>evil eye <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17219AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17219AI\"></sup>hastens after wealthAnd does not know that want will come upon him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17220AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17220AJ\"></sup>rebukes a man will afterward find <i>more</i> favorThan he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17220AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17220AK\"></sup>flatters with the tongue.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17221AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17221AL\"></sup>robs his father or his motherAnd says, “It is not a transgression,”Is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17221AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17221AM\"></sup>companion of a man who destroys.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>An arrogant man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17222AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17222AN\"></sup>stirs up strife,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17222AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17222AO\"></sup>trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17222AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17222AP\"></sup>will prosper.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17223AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17223AQ\"></sup>trusts in his own heart is a fool,But he who walks wisely will be delivered.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17224AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17224AR\"></sup>gives to the poor will never want,But he who shuts his eyes will have many curses.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When the wicked rise, men hide themselves;But when they perish, the righteous increase."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>A man who hardens <i>his</i> neck after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17226A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17226A\"></sup>much reproofWill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17226B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17226B\"></sup>suddenly be broken beyond remedy.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17227C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17227C\"></sup>righteous increase, the people rejoice,But when a wicked man rules, people groan.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17228D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17228D\"></sup>loves wisdom makes his father glad,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17228E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17228E\"></sup>keeps company with harlots wastes <i>his</i> wealth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17229F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17229F\"></sup>king gives stability to the land by justice,But a man who takes bribes overthrows it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17230G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17230G\"></sup>flatters his neighborIs spreading a net for his steps.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>By transgression an evil man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17231H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17231H\"></sup>ensnared,But the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17231I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17231I\"></sup>sings and rejoices.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17232J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17232J\"></sup>righteous is concerned for the rights of the poor,The wicked does not understand <i>such</i> concern.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Scorners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17233K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17233K\"></sup>set a city aflame,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17233L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17233L\"></sup>wise men turn away anger.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When a wise man has a controversy with a foolish man,The foolish man either rages or laughs, and there is no rest.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17235M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17235M\"></sup>bloodshed hate the blameless,But the upright are concerned for his life.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17236N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17236N\"></sup>fool always loses his temper,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17236O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17236O\"></sup>wise man holds it back.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17237P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17237P\"></sup>ruler pays attention to falsehood,All his ministers <i>become</i> wicked.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17238Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17238Q\"></sup>poor man and the oppressor have this in common:The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17238R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17238R\"></sup>light to the eyes of both.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17239S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17239S\"></sup>king judges the poor with truth,His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17239T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17239T\"></sup>throne will be established forever.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17240U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17240U\"></sup>rod and reproof give wisdom,But a child who gets his own way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17240V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17240V\"></sup>brings shame to his mother.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When the wicked increase, transgression increases;But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17241W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17241W\"></sup>righteous will see their fall.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17242X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17242X\"></sup>Correct your son, and he will give you comfort;He will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17242Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17242Y\"></sup>delight your soul.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Where there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17243Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17243Z\"></sup>no vision, the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17243AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17243AA\"></sup>are unrestrained,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17243AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17243AB\"></sup>happy is he who keeps the law.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A slave will not be instructed by words <i>alone</i>;For though he understands, there will be no response.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do you see a man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17245AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17245AC\"></sup>hasty in his words?There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17245AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17245AD\"></sup>more hope for a fool than for him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He who pampers his slave from childhoodWill in the end find him to be a son.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17247AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17247AE\"></sup>angry man stirs up strife,And a hot-tempered man abounds in transgression.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A man’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17248AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17248AF\"></sup>pride will bring him low,But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17248AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17248AG\"></sup>humble spirit will obtain honor.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He who is a partner with a thief hates his own life;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17249AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17249AH\"></sup>hears the oath but tells nothing.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17250AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17250AI\"></sup>fear of man brings a snare,But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17250AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17250AJ\"></sup>trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be exalted.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17251AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17251AK\"></sup>Many seek the ruler’s favor,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17251AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17251AL\"></sup>justice for man <i>comes</i> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17252AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17252AM\"></sup>unjust man is abominable to the righteous,And he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17252AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17252AN\"></sup>upright in the way is abominable to the wicked."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The words of Agur the son of Jakeh, the oracle.The man declares to Ithiel, to Ithiel and Ucal:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely I am more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17254A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17254A\"></sup>stupid than any man,And I do not have the understanding of a man.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Neither have I learned wisdom,Nor do I have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17255B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17255B\"></sup>knowledge of the Holy One.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17256C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17256C\"></sup>ascended into heaven and descended?Who has gathered the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17256D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17256D\"></sup>wind in His fists?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17256E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17256E\"></sup>wrapped the waters in His garment?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17256F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17256F\"></sup>established all the ends of the earth?What is His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17256G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17256G\"></sup>name or His son’s name?Surely you know!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17257H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17257H\"></sup>word of God is tested;He is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17257I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17257I\"></sup>shield to those who take refuge in Him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17258J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17258J\"></sup>Do not add to His wordsOr He will reprove you, and you will be proved a liar.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Two things I asked of You,Do not refuse me before I die:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Keep deception and lies far from me,Give me neither poverty nor riches;Feed me with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17260K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17260K\"></sup>food that is my portion,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>That I not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17261L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17261L\"></sup>full and deny <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17261M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17261M\"></sup><i>You</i> and say, “Who is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”Or that I not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17261N\"></sup>in want and steal,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17261O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17261O\"></sup>profane the name of my God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not slander a slave to his master,Or he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17262P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17262P\"></sup>curse you and you will be found guilty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There is a kind of <i>man</i> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17263Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17263Q\"></sup>curses his fatherAnd does not bless his mother.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There is a kind who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17264R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17264R\"></sup>pure in his own eyes,Yet is not washed from his filthiness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There is a kind—oh how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17265S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17265S\"></sup>lofty are his eyes!And his eyelids are raised <i>in arrogance</i>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There is a kind of <i>man</i> whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17266T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17266T\"></sup>teeth are <i>like</i> swordsAnd his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17266U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17266U\"></sup>jaw teeth <i>like</i> knives,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17266V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17266V\"></sup>devour the afflicted from the earthAnd the needy from among men.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The leech has two daughters,“Give,” “Give.”There are three things that will not be satisfied,Four that will not say, “Enough”:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17268W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17268W\"></sup>Sheol, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17268X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17268X\"></sup>barren womb,Earth that is never satisfied with water,And fire that never says, “Enough.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The eye that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17269Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17269Y\"></sup>mocks a fatherAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17269Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17269Z\"></sup>scorns a mother,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17269AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17269AA\"></sup>ravens of the valley will pick it out,And the young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17269AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17269AB\"></sup>eagles will eat it.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There are three things which are too wonderful for me,Four which I do not understand:",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The way of an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17271AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17271AC\"></sup>eagle in the sky,The way of a serpent on a rock,The way of a ship in the middle of the sea,And the way of a man with a maid.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>This is the way of an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17272AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17272AD\"></sup>adulterous woman:She eats and wipes her mouth,And says, “I have done no wrong.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Under three things the earth quakes,And under four, it cannot bear up:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Under a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17274AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17274AE\"></sup>slave when he becomes king,And a fool when he is satisfied with food,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Under an unloved woman when she gets a husband,And a maidservant when she supplants her mistress.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Four things are small on the earth,But they are exceedingly wise:",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17277AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17277AF\"></sup>ants are not a strong people,But they prepare their food in the summer;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17278AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17278AG\"></sup>shephanim are not mighty people,Yet they make their houses in the rocks;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The locusts have no king,Yet all of them go out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17279AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17279AH\"></sup>ranks;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The lizard you may grasp with the hands,Yet it is in kings’ palaces.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>There are three things which are stately in <i>their</i> march,Even four which are stately when they walk:",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The lion <i>which</i> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17282AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17282AI\"></sup>mighty among beastsAnd does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17282AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17282AJ\"></sup>retreat before any,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The strutting rooster, the male goat also,And a king <i>when his</i> army is with him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If you have been foolish in exalting yourselfOr if you have plotted <i>evil</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17284AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17284AK\"></sup><i>put your</i> hand on your mouth.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For the churning of milk produces butter,And pressing the nose brings forth blood;So the churning of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17285AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17285AL\"></sup>anger produces strife."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>The words of King Lemuel, the oracle which his mother taught him:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>What, O my son?And what, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17287A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17287A\"></sup>son of my womb?And what, O son of my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17287B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17287B\"></sup>vows?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17288C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17288C\"></sup>Do not give your strength to women,Or your ways to that which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17288D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17288D\"></sup>destroys kings.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is not for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17289E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17289E\"></sup>kings, O Lemuel,It is not for kings to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17289F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17289F\"></sup>drink wine,Or for rulers to desire strong drink,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For they will drink and forget what is decreed,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17290G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17290G\"></sup>pervert the rights of all the afflicted.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Give strong drink to him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17291H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17291H\"></sup>perishing,And wine to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17291I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17291I\"></sup>whose life is bitter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let him drink and forget his povertyAnd remember his trouble no more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17293J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17293J\"></sup>Open your mouth for the mute,For the rights of all the unfortunate.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Open your mouth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17294K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17294K\"></sup>judge righteously,And defend the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17294L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17294L\"></sup>rights of the afflicted and needy.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17295M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17295M\"></sup>excellent wife, who can find?For her worth is far <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17295N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17295N\"></sup>above jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The heart of her husband trusts in her,And he will have no lack of gain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>She does him good and not evilAll the days of her life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She looks for wool and flaxAnd works with her hands in delight.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17299O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17299O\"></sup>merchant ships;She brings her food from afar.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17300P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17300P\"></sup>rises also while it is still nightAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17300Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17300Q\"></sup>gives food to her householdAnd portions to her maidens.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>She considers a field and buys it;From her earnings she plants a vineyard.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17302R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17302R\"></sup>girds herself with strengthAnd makes her arms strong.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She senses that her gain is good;Her lamp does not go out at night.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>She stretches out her hands to the distaff,And her hands grasp the spindle.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17305S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17305S\"></sup>extends her hand to the poor,And she stretches out her hands to the needy.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>She is not afraid of the snow for her household,For all her household are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17306T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17306T\"></sup>clothed with scarlet.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>She makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17307U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17307U\"></sup>coverings for herself;Her clothing is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17307V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17307V\"></sup>fine linen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17307W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17307W\"></sup>purple.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Her husband is known <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17308X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17308X\"></sup>in the gates,When he sits among the elders of the land.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>She makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17309Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17309Y\"></sup>linen garments and sells <i>them</i>,And supplies belts to the tradesmen.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Strength and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17310Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17310Z\"></sup>dignity are her clothing,And she smiles at the future.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17311AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17311AA\"></sup>opens her mouth in wisdom,And the teaching of kindness is on her tongue.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She looks well to the ways of her household,And does not eat the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17312AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17312AB\"></sup>bread of idleness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Her children rise up and bless her;Her husband <i>also</i>, and he praises her, <i>saying</i>:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Many daughters have done nobly,But you excel them all.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Charm is deceitful and beauty is vain,<i>But</i> a woman who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17315AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17315AC\"></sup>fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, she shall be praised.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Give her the product of her hands,And let her works praise her in the gates."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;